\v 16 Kot…®tun …ôsas m…ôm…ô s…ôn…ôm…ô in t…ômasitu e nagelo m…®n, m…ôto in t…ômasitu e noanol m…®n r…ôha Epraham.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Aes 41:8-9; Luk 3:8\f*   
\p
\v 17 Iesu t…ôike mos n…®p…ôt…®n ne n…®tan n…ôhlan, m…ôm…ô in otuwa mol tahmen e pian m…®n e nol…ôn m…®n rafin,\f + \fr 2:17 \ft Fil 2:7; Hip 2:10; 4:15; 5:1,8-9\f* m…ôm…ô in t…®tun nas…ôkitun…ôn\f + \fr 2:17 \ft Hip 5:2\f* kitat, k…ôn koatag…®le lan. In ot…ôk…ôike muwa mol n…ôhlan, t…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô in pris asol ag…®n pahrien, tatol w…ôk r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn m…ôm…ô in ot…®lp…®n nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n.  
\v 18 K…ôn roiu …ôh, nian Setan tatos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat, k…ôn Iesu t…®tun nasitu…ôn elat, m…ôto-inu in m…®n, in t…®n…ôto t…ôrat r…ôk…®s nian Setan t…ômos-ip…ôn-os-ip…ôn k…ôm in.\f + \fr 2:18 \ft Hip 4:15\f*   
\c 3  
\s1 Iesu in tapr…ôk…®s-in Moses  
\m
\v 1 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n, Uhg…®n t…®naun-in\f + \fr 3:1 \ft Rom 8:28\f* k…ôl…ôh kitat min it…ômat o nuw…®n…ôn e nego e neai, k…ôn mol m…ôm…ô kitat net…ôm iasim. M…ôto-inu Iesu t…ôtasitu nulan e kitat, it…ômat on…ôkot…ôk…ôike kat…ôt…ôl…®g-in p…®k Iesu …ôh, in aposol k…ôn in pris asol ag…®n r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn r…ôhatat it…ôm kitat koat…ôn-iar…ôp.  
\v 2 Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr Iesu m…ôm…ô in otol w…ôk u, k…ôn in t…ômol n…ôwia Uhg…®n e nat…®mnat rafin, tahmen e Moses aup…ôn t…ômol n…ôwia Uhg…®n e r…ôhan w…ôk rafin, m…ôm…ô in otatehm w…®r nim…ô, inu net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Nam 12:7\f*  
\v 3 Ilau k…ôr…ôn k…ôtioal n…ôwia Uhg…®n, m…ôto et…ôm t…ômil…ôk…®n nim…ô, net…ômim koat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…®n ron tapr…ôk…®s-in nim…ô it…ôm in t…ômol. K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, t…ôtuat…®p m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr Iesu tapr…ôk…®s-in Moses.  
\v 4 K…ôn nim…ô m…®n rafin, net…ômim koatil…ôk…®n, m…ôto Uhg…®n in t…ômil…ôk…®n nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm t…ôtat…®g.  
\v 5 Moses in iolw…ôk kit e n…®p…ôgnoa nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm tatol n…ôwia Uhg…®n, matehm nim…ô r…ôhan, inu net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n. K…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Moses tat…ôpsen-p…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm Uhg…®n ot…ôpan…ôg…ôtun.  
\v 6 Kristo, in m…®n tatol n…ôwia Uhg…®n. M…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô in iolw…ôk …ôm kit tahmen e Moses. In N…ôt…®n, k…ôn tatos nep…ôt…ôn o n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn e r…ôhan nim…ô. K…ôn ok…ôm…ô kitat k…ôsot…ôg…®n…ôn, k…ôn motalkut m…ôm…ô okot…ôtul …ôskas…®k\f + \fr 3:6 \ft Hip 3:14; 4:14; Rom 11:22\f* o nat un it…ôm kitat k…ômot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhatat lan, k…ôn motausit ron, k…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat u, net…ômim r…ôhan, kitat r…ôhan nim…ô.\f + \fr 3:6 \ft 1 Kor 3:16; 1 Pita 2:5\f*   
\s1 Oatehm m…ôha-m…ôha it…ômat m…®n e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat  
\p
\v 7 N…ôghat…ôn u inu, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúRoiu …ôm, on…ôkot…ôk…ôike moat…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôwian,   
\q1
\v 8 m…ôsotol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat-kap…ô t…ôskas…®k p…®k,  
\q1 tahmen e t…®p…®t…ômat m…®n ilat k…ômoatol mihin aup…ôn moat…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n,  
\q1 nian ilat k…ômoatek asg…ôw…®n Uhg…®n e ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Eks 17:1-7; Nam 20:2-5\f*   
\q1
\v 9 Ik…®n …ôh, t…®p…®t…ômat m…®n k…ômot…ôk…ôike k…ôm io m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan r…ôhak n…ôsan…ôn…ôn,  
\q1 nat …ôpnap…®n ilat k…ômot…ôplan pap nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm emol o nup foti.\f + \fr 3:9 \ft Nam 14:3; Dut 1:3; W…ôk 7:36\f*   
\q1
\v 10 K…ôn io iatol nem…ôha k…ôm ilat, k…ôn mat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòN…®kilat t…ôtan is…ôu ron io nian rafin.  
\q1 K…ôn ilat motap…ôs nol…ôn nat it…ôm iat…ôn k…ôm ilat.‚Äô   
\q1
\v 11 Nem…ôha t…ômol io,  
\q1 k…ôn ekos noanaw…®l kit m…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòIlat okol k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn e ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron io ik…®n.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Nam 14:21-23\f* \f + \fr 3:11 \ft Sam 95:7-11\f*   
\p
\v 12 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n, oatehm w…®r it…ômat m…®n o nat u. Otol m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat at…®p ot…ôs…ôrat…ôn k…ôn kit t…ôsap…ôs…ôn nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, mol m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…ôuhlin-p…ôn it…ômat is…ôu o Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…ômeg…ôh.  
\v 13 Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn ‚ÄúRoiu …ôm,‚Äù k…ôn nian u ‚Äúroiu‚Äù t…ôtat…®g …ôh. Tol n…ôhlan, n…ôkot…ôk…ôike moat…ôghat roiu k…ôm it…ômat m…®n, moatehm m…ôha-m…ôha it…ômat m…®n nian rafin, m…ôm…ô nol…ôn rat ot…ôseiu…ô-in…ôn it…ômat kit mol r…ôhn-kap…ô t…ôskas…®k o Uhg…®n.  
\v 14 M…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôtul t…®mt…®m m…ôtoarus-p…ôn namnun, motahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n t…ôskas…®k mi…ôk…®s, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inu k…ômot…ôtuoun motahat…ôt…ô wi …ôm lan, k…ôn tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô kitat k…®noatos k…ôl…ôh nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôha Kristo.  
\v 15 M…ôto sotaluin…ôn n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm k…ôm…ôn,  
\q1 ‚ÄúRoiu …ôm, on…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôwian  
\q1 m…ôsotol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat-kap…ô t…ôskas…®k p…®k,  
\q1 tahmen e t…®p…®t…ômat m…®n ilat k…ômoatol mihin aup…ôn  
\q1 moat…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:15 \ft Sam 95:7-8; Hip 3:7-8\f*   
\p
\v 16 ?K…ôn pah m…®n un it…ôm k…ômot…ôto pap n…ôwia Uhg…®n, m…ôsotol…ôn? Ilat un Moses t…ômit-ir…ôk…®s ilat Ijip.\f + \fr 3:16 \ft Nam 14:1-35\f*  
\v 17 ?Pah m…®n un k…ômotol Uhg…®n nem…ôha tol o nup foti? Ilat un, net…ôm k…ômotol nol…ôn rat, k…ôn moat…ôme mot…®m…®s moat…ôm…ôhl …ôpnap…®n …ôm …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n.\f + \fr 3:17 \ft Nam 14:29; 1 Kor 10:1-13\f*  
\v 18 ?K…ôn pah m…®n un Uhg…®n t…ômat…ôghat k…ôm ilat, matos noanaw…®l m…ôm…ô ilat ok…ôsotuw…®n…ôn motiet-ar…ôp…ôn ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n? In t…ômat…ôghat k…ôm net…ôm k…ômot…ôht n…ôwian.\f + \fr 3:18 \ft Nam 14:22-23; Sam 95:11; Hip 3:11\f*  
\v 19 K…ôn kitat koat…ôplan m…ôm…ô k…ôm…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn ilat m…ôm…ô okotiet-ar…ôp…ôn ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ik…®n ron, m…ôto-inu ilat k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan.   
\c 4  
\s1 Ik…®n katos nameg…ôn o Uhg…®n ik…®n  
\m
\v 1 M…ôto kitat u, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô kitat kot…®tun nuw…®n…ôn im…ô ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n, k…ôn n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn u, tat…ôtul …ôh, mater…ôh otat. Tol n…ôhlan, p…ôs kitat koat…ôto itat, k…ôn moat…ôg…®n m…ôm…ô kitat kit okol m…ôtan t…ôsos…ôn nameg…ôn …ôh.  
\v 2 M…ôto-inu kitat k…®not…ôto r…ôk…®s namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô ik…®n kit o nameg…ôn r…ôhatat, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inu net…ôm aup…ôn k…ômot…ôto n…ôghat…ôn mihin. M…ôto n…ôghat…ôn …ôh, t…ôm…ôsasitu…ôn elat, m…ôto-inu ilat k…ômoat…ôto …ôm, m…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan.  
\v 3 M…ôto-inu kitat net…ôm k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôm lan, kitat kot…®tun nuw…®n…ôn im…ô, ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n. M…ôto r…ôha net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm k…ôsotahat…ôt…ô…ôn lan, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúNem…ôha t…ômol io, k…ôn ekos noanaw…®l kit, m…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòIlat okol k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron io ik…®n.‚Äô‚Äù\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Sam 95:11; Hip 3:11\f*  
\m T…ôm…ôn n…ôhlan, nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô t…®nol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô r…ôk…®s ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n nian in t…ôm…ôtuoun matol n…ôtueint…ôn.  
\v 4 Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô t…®nol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô r…ôk…®s lan, m…ôto-inu Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n in tat…ôghat-in Sapat, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúT…ômol n…ôtueint…ôn, k…ôn e nian sep…®n lan, Uhg…®n t…ômameg e r…ôhan w…ôk.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:4 \ft Jen 2:2\f*  
\v 5 M…ôto ik…®n m…®n neen e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIlat okol k…ôsotuw…®n…ôn ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron io ik…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Sam 95:11\f*   
\p
\v 6 Tol n…ôhlan, ik…®n katos nameg…ôn o Uhg…®n ik…®n …ôh, in t…ôtat…®g …ôh m…ôm…ô net…ômim okotuw…®n ik…®n. M…ôto net…ôm m…®n u aup…ôn it…ôm k…ômot…ôto namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r, ilat k…ômot…ôm…®k-ar…ôp…ôn-in nuw…®n…ôn ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n, m…ôto-inu k…ômot…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n.  
\v 7 K…ônu, uaris…®g lan, tol-p…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu m…®n nian kit m…®n o nuw…®n…ôn ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n. Nian …ôh, inu roiu. Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp nat u k…ôm Tef…®t m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúRoiu …ôm, on…ôkot…ôk…ôike mot…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôwian  
\q1 m…ôsotol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat-kap…ô t…ôskas…®k p…®k.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:7 \ft Sam 95:7-8; Hip 3:7-8\f*   
\m
\v 8 N…®kit…ômat tu…ôh-tu suah u Josua\f + \fr 4:8 \ft Josua in n…ôrg…®n kit e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Isrel. K…ôn n…ôrg…®n u Iesu, n…ôrg…®lau tahmen-ahmen …ôm e Josua e n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha net…ôm Kris. Nian Josua t…ômos-ip…ôn nameg…ôn k…ôm net…ôm Isrel …ôp…ôh Kenan, n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Josua in tat…ôpsen-p…ôn nat it…ôm Iesu ot…ôpanol, mos-ipa nameg…ôn pahrien k…ôm kitat.\f* aup…ôn. Ok…ôm…ô Josua t…ômos-ip…ôn nameg…ôn k…ôm ilat nian in t…ômit ilat moatuw…®n Kenan, k…ônu Uhg…®n okol t…ôs…ôn m…®n…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôl…ôh…ôu nian kit m…®n m…ôm…ô in nian r…ôha nuw…®n…ôn im…ô ik…®n katos nameg…ôn ron ik…®n.\f + \fr 4:8 \ft Dut 31:7; Jos 22:4\f*  
\v 9 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôn nian p…®s…®n kit m…®n, nian …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g …ôh o r…ôhan net…ômim m…ôm…ô okotuw…®n motos nameg…ôn, e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômameg mihin e r…ôhan w…ôk m…®n aup…ôn, e nian r…ôha Sapat.  
\v 10 M…ôto-inu et…ôm tatuw…®n im…ô m…ôm…ô otos nameg…ôn u, in otameg e r…ôhan w…ôk, tahmen …ôm e Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ômameg e r…ôhan w…ôk aup…ôn.\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Jen 2:2; Hip 4:4\f*  
\v 11 O nat u, kitat okotalkut …ôskas…®k m…ôm…ô okotuw…®n im…ô motos nameg…ôn u. T…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat kit, ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha net…ôm aup…ôn it…ôm k…ômot…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n, moat…ôme.   
\p
\v 12 M…ôto-inu Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 4:12 \ft 1 Pita 1:23; Aes 49:2; Nol ∆èp…ôn 19:13-15; Jon 12:48\f* in tat…ômeg…ôh m…ôsan…ôn m…®tahl…ôp…®k e w…ôk r…ôhan.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Aes 55:11; Jer 23:29\f* K…ôn in tahmen e naip tas…®l…ô e n…®kal…®n k…ôr…ôn mil.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Efes 6:17\f* In t…®tun n…ôtarer…ôh…ôn mat…ôplan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n ne n…®kin p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n e net…ômim, tahmen …ôm e naip it…ôm tat…ôtarer…ôh mat…ôplan ik…®n tat…®lp…®n m…®n ik…®n e n…®k…®lk…®lit…ôm ne n…ôhau im…ô ag…®n. In t…ôtakil n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…®n ne nol…ôn anion m…®n e n…®kit…ôm.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft 1 Kor 4:5\f*  
\v 13 Uhg…®n tat…ôplan nat…®mnat rafin e n…ôtueint…ôn tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô k…ôm…ôte k…®talkin-…®talkin katep…®k, koat…ôm…ôhl pi…ôpi…ô …ôm. Kitat okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôn-iar…ôp rafin ag…®n nat…®mnat it…ôm k…ômotol k…ôm Uhg…®n u inu.\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 2:23\f*   
\s1 Iesu in t…ômuwa pris asol ag…®n it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s, m…ôto-inu in Uhg…®n pap, m…ôto t…ômuwa et…ômim  
\p
\v 14 Tol n…ôhlan, p…ôs kitat kotask…ôl…®m-i…ôk…®s nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhatat it…ôm k…®noat…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s, m…ôto-inu kitat koatos pris asol ag…®n kit r…ôhatat in iahgin. Inu Iesu, N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, it…ôm t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s im…ô e nego e neai.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Hip 7:25\f*  
\v 15 M…ôto-inu r…ôhatat pris asol ag…®n, in Pris kit it…ôm tat…ôto w…®r n…®kitat, mat…ôto w…®r ot…ôhrol kitat k…ôsotahmen…ôn, m…ôto-inu nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm tatek asg…ôw…®n kitat e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, nat…®mnat kiti…ôh m…®n …ôm, k…®notek asg…ôw…®n r…ôk…®s in e r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. R…ôhatat pris asol ag…®n, in t…®n…®tun r…ôk…®s r…ôhatat n…ôpou…ôn m…®n.\f + \fr 4:15 \ft Hip 2:17\f* M…ôto nat kiti…ôh …ôm un, in t…ôsol…ôn nat t…ôrat kit.  
\v 16 O nat u, p…ôs kitat k…ôsot…ôg…®n…ôn o nuwam…ôn iu…ôhk…®r o jea r…ôha kig\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Jea r…ôha kig u, in Uhg…®n tat…ôp…ôl…ôh ik…®n, k…ôn mat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, m…ôto o nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm Iesu t…ômol, jea r…ôha kig u, in tatuwa tahmen e Ik…®n Kat…®lp…®n Nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n Ik…®n it…ôm Oltesteman tat…ôghat-in (Onakehm e Eks 25:18-22; Lev 16:1-15). Ik…®n …ôh in…ôh, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôtas…ôkitun k…ônu mat…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôhan ik…®n k…ôm itat k…ôn m…ôtaf…ôl r…ôk…®s nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhatat. In t…®tun nol…ôn e n…®ta Iesu it…ôm t…ômaiu otat, k…ôn t…ôm…ôr…ôk…®n-r…ôk…®n r…ôhan nem…ôha.\f* u, t…ôtawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm kitat. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, in otas…ôkitun itat, k…ôn mos-ipa n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm kitat e n…®kin agien, e nian r…ôha n…ôrat…ôn otuwa otat.\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Eks 25:18-22; Lev 16:2,14,15; Hip 9:5\f*   
\c 5  
\m
\v 1 Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô nian rafin Uhg…®n tat…®t…ôpun suah kit k…ôn mat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr in m…ôm…ô otuwa pris asol ag…®n, m…ôm…ô in suat…®p r…ôha net…ômim okotuw…®n o Uhg…®n. In suat…®p r…ôhalat o nos-ip…ôn…ôn nat…®mnat k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn in matol sakrifais o r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n.\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Hip 2:17; 7:27; 8:3; 9:9\f*\fig |alt="Incense altar and high priest in tabernacle" src="HK00267B.TIF" size="col" loc="Heb 5:1" ref="Hip 5:1" \fig*  
\v 2 Roiu …ôh, m…ôto-inu pris asol ag…®n u in et…ômim kit, in t…®tun nol…ôn t…®m…ôt…®g …ôm o net…ômim,\f + \fr 5:2 \ft Hip 2:17-18\f* nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô ilat kot…ôruru ag…®n nat it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p, ilat kotag…®m r…ôk…®s e suat…®p, m…ôto-inu in m…®n, in t…ôsahmen…ôn, in tatol t…ôfag…ô rat\f + \fr 5:2 \ft Hip 4:15; 7:28\f* nian tep…ôt.  
\v 3 In tatol t…ôfag…ô rat n…ôhlan, k…ôn tol m…ôm…ô e nian r…ôha sakrifais, in ot…ôk…ôike mol sakrifais o r…ôhan at…®p t…ôfag…ô, k…ôn mat…®g mol m…®n r…ôha net…ômim m…®n.\f + \fr 5:3 \ft Lev 9:7; 16:6-15; Hip 7:27; 9:7\f*   
\p
\v 4 Suah kit okol t…ôs…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô in otol w…ôk r…ôha pris asol ag…®n, mat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr at…®p in. K…ôp…ô, Uhg…®n ot…ôk…ôike maun-in r…ôhan kit et…ômim m…ôm…ô in otol w…ôk u, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inu t…ômaun-in mihin Eron aup…ôn.\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Hip 5:1-4 koat…ôghat-in …ôtuat…®p w…ôk it…ôm pris asol ag…®n m…®n k…ômotol aup…ôn, muwa m…ôtoarus nian net…ôm Rom k…ômot…ôr…ôk…®n Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n e nup fote t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s uaris…®g Iesu t…ôpan…®m…®s.\f* \f + \fr 5:4 \ft Eks 28:1; Nam 18:7\f*  
\v 5 Tol n…ôhlan, Kristo in t…ôm…®s…®l…ôs-ip…ôr at…®p…ôn in m…ôm…ô in pris asol ag…®n. M…ôto Uhg…®n in t…ôm…®t…ôpun, k…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIk n…ôt…®k.  
\q1 Roiu enuwa r…ôham tata …ôtuat…®p.‚Äù\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Sam 2:7; W…ôk 13:33; Hip 1:5\f*   
\m
\v 6 K…ôn ik…®n kit m…®n e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Sam 110:4\f* in tat…ôn m…ôm…ô  
\q1 ‚ÄúIk pris kit tahmen e Melkisetek aup…ôn,\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Jen 14:18-20; Sek 6:13; Hip 5:10; 6:20; 7:1-22\f*\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Melkisetek (Jen 14:18) in kig r…ôha Salem (Salem u, n…®p…ôt…®n u, N…ôm…ôlinu…ôn) k…ôn in pris r…ôha Uhg…®n Il…®s P…®k. In t…ôm…ôtat…®g e nian r…ôha Epraham. Kristo in tahmen e Melkisetek m…ôto-inu in pris ne in kig m…®n. M…ôto noanol r…ôha Eron m…®n, ilat pris m…®n …ôm, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô kig m…®n; Hip 7:2.\f*  
\q1 k…ôn ik onakatol w…ôk r…ôha pris nian rafin,  
\q1 matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 7 E n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha Kristo e n…ôtueint…ôn u, in tat…ôfak k…ôm Uhg…®n, mat…ôtap…ôh-in nasitu…ôn, m…ôtas…ôk …ôf…ôm…ôh, nahui n…ômt…®n t…®tai…ôh. Uhg…®n tatos n…ôsan…ôn…ôn o nosmeg…ôh…ôn in e n…®m…®s…ôn. K…ôn in t…ômat…®siai-in Uhg…®n, k…ôn matol n…ôwian,\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Luk 22:42\f* k…ôn o nat u, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôto in.\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Mat 26:36-46; Mak 14:32-42; Luk 22:39-46\f*  
\v 8 Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô Kristo in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôto nahm…ô…ôn. Tol n…ôhlan, nahm…ô…ôn r…ôha Iesu, t…ômol in t…®tun w…®r n…®p…ôt…® nol…ôn n…ôwia Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 5:8 \ft Fil 2:6-8\f*  
\v 9 k…ôn t…ômuwa et…ôm …ôtuat…®p r…ôha nol…ôn w…ôk r…ôha pris asol ag…®n r…ôhatat. K…ôn in t…ômol suat…®p o nosmeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n r…ôhan net…ôm m…®n u koatol n…ôwian, matos w…®r ilat, matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô.  
\v 10 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôr…®g u k…ôm in, m…ôm…ô in pris asol ag…®n tahmen …ôm e suah u Melkisetek aup…ôn.\f + \fr 5:10 \ft Sam 110:4; Hip 5:6\f*   
\p
\v 11 It…®mat emotos n…ôghat…ôn tep…ôt m…ô ekot…ôn-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôm…ô Iesu in pris asol ag…®n tahmen e Melkisetek. M…ôto ti…ôk…®s p…®k o n…ôn w…®r…ôn ilat rafin k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôto-inun it…ômat n…ôkoat…ôlpah-in p…®k n…ôto…ôn nat kit k…ôn m…®tun.  
\v 12 It…ômat n…ômotahat…ôt…ô nuw…ôh r…ôk…®s, k…ôn t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…®notuwa r…ôk…®s i…ôg…ôtun m…®n r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. M…ôto k…ôp…ô, it…ômat n…ôkoatol …ôm nulan. Roiu …ôh, k…ôike k…ôg…ôtun m…®n it…ômat, t…ôtuoun m…®n e n…ôuk…ôt…®n n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n. N…®pahrien…ôn u, it…ômat n…®notahmen-in r…ôk…®s nun…ôn nagw…ôn…ôn …ôskas…®k m…®n, m…ôto n…ôkotahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô k…ôtapinahin …ôh it…ômat.\f + \fr 5:12 \ft 1 Pita 2:2\f*  
\v 13 M…ôto e net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koat…ômah …ôh n…ôhlan, ilat u n…®sualk…ôl…ôh m…ôtm…ôt…®g, it…ôm koat…ôk…ôku …ôh, k…ôsotenat…®g w…®r…ôn …ôh o n…®tun…ôn n…ôg…ôtun…ôn m…®n r…ôha nol…ôn …ôtuat…®p.  
\v 14 M…ôto nagw…ôn…ôn …ôskas…®k in n…®g…® net…ôm r…ôhalat n…®tun…ôn t…®n…®m…ôt…ô r…ôk…®s, it…ôm k…ômotiuw r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn o n…®tun…ôn nat…®mnat p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p ne it…ôm t…ôrat, k…ôn ilat moatol it…ôm t…ôw…®r,\f + \fr 5:14 \ft Rom 16:19\f* in …ôm in …ôm.   
\c 6  
\m
\v 1 Tol nulan, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô kitat ok…ôsot…ôg…ôtun m…®n…ôn n…ôuk…ôt…®\f + \fr 6:1 \ft Hip 5:12\f* n…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Kristo, m…ôto p…ôs kitat okoat…ôk…ôike moatuw…®n m…ôm…ô okot…®m…ôt…ô e Iesu Kristo. Kitat k…®not…ôuhlin r…ôk…®s kitat e nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm kot…®tun nit-ip…ôn…ôn item e n…®m…®s…ôn.\f + \fr 6:1 \ft Hip 9:14\f* Kitat k…®notahat…ôt…ô r…ôk…®s e Uhg…®n. Tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô k…®notaf…ôl r…ôk…®s n…ôme nim…ô. Nian …ôh-roiu in r…ôha n…ôgp…ôhap-in…ôn nim…ô.  
\v 2 Kitat k…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s n…ôg…ôtun…ôn m…®n r…ôha nol…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n r…ôha naikuas…ôn, k…ôn m…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s n…ôg…ôtun…ôn m…®n r…ôha n…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn…ôn nelm…®t…ôm e r…ôhn-kap…ô et…ômim, o n…ôfak…ôn lan. K…ôn kitat k…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô kitat okot…ôtul m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn mot…®tun m…®n m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otakil net…ômim, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn nalp…®n…ôn lil…®n r…ôhan k…ôm net…ôm kotol t…ôfag…ô rat. Nat…®mnat m…®n u, kitat k…®not…ôghat-in r…ôk…®s, t…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô kitat koat…®s…®mat…®p e n…ôghat…ôn kiti…ôh m…®n …ôm nian rafin.  
\v 3 Tol nulan m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômeg…ôhan-in …ôm k…ôm kitat, k…ôn kitat okotuwa net…ôm k…®not…®m…ôt…ô r…ôk…®s.   
\p
\v 4 ?Okotalkut m…ôm…ô okotol nulan, m…ôto t…ôhrol e net…ômim it…ôm k…ômotuwa o Uhg…®n m…ôto roiu k…®notap…ôs Uhg…®n mot…ôuhlin m…®n m…ôntaalat o Kristo? Ilat …ôh, ilat net…ôm k…ômotehm n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn,\f + \fr 6:4 \ft Hip 10:32\f* k…ôn k…®notun asg…ôw…®n r…ôk…®s noan e nego e neai it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ipa,\f + \fr 6:4 \ft Efes 2:8\f* k…ôn m…®noat…®tun m…ôm…ô in t…ôw…®r, k…ôn m…®noatos r…ôk…®s o Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 6:4 \ft Kal 3:2\f*  
\v 5 K…ôn ilat u, net…ôm k…®notun asg…ôw…®n r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n in t…ôw…®r,\f + \fr 6:5 \ft Sam 34:8\f* ilat k…®not…ôto r…ôk…®s n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn tuwa.  
\v 6 M…ôto ok…ôm…ô ilat k…ômot…ôuhlin m…ôntaalat o Uhg…®n, suat…®p kit t…®k…ô m…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôuhlin-pa m…®n ilat o Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 6:6 \ft 2 Pita 2:21\f* Ilat k…ômot…ôr…ôk…®n at…®p …ôm ilat, m…ôto-inu tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô k…®not…ôht-ip…ôn m…®n …ôm N…ôt…® Uhg…®n e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, moat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr m…®n e n…®gan…ômt…® net…ômim, k…ôn ilat k…®noatol m…®n m…®l…ô lan, moat…ôr…ôk…®n.   
\p
\v 7 N…®kim tu…ôh-tu nat u. N…ôpt…ôn u tatos w…®r nuhu…ôn it…ôm tat…ôf…®k, k…ôn in nagw…ôn…ôn tep…ôt lan n…®g…® net…ôm m…®n un, koatol w…ôk ik…®n. Uhg…®n n…®kin tagien p…®k ron, k…ôn n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôhan t…ôtat…®g lan.  
\v 8 M…ôto n…®m…ôpt…ôn rat it…ôm t…ôsos…ôn nat w…®r tep…ôt lan, k…ôn iap…®l-iap…®l ne k…®ras …ôm katu…ôwi…ô lan. N…ôpt…ôn …ôh t…®n…ôs…ôw…®r m…®n…ôn o nat kit. T…®n…ôtaiu …ôm o n…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn. E namnun, n…®g…ôm otus nat…®mnat it…ôm kotat…®g lan.   
\p
\v 9 Piak m…®n, nat …ôpnap…®n io iat…ôghat nulan k…ôm it…ômat, m…ôto ek…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôsotahmen…ôn e n…ôpt…ôn rat …ôh. Ek…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô it…ômat noatos nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat m…ôto-inun in tatosmeg…ôh it…ômat.  
\v 10 Uhg…®n okol t…ôsaluin…ôn r…ôhat…ômat w…ôk m…®n n…ômoatol m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n r…ôhan nol…ôn t…ôtuat…®p …ôm nian rafin. K…ôn okol in t…ôsol…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n e nol…ôn w…®r r…ôha nolkeike…ôn it…ôm n…ômotol k…ôm in, k…ôn moatol …ôh, nian n…ômotasitu e r…ôhan net…ômim.\f + \fr 6:10 \ft Mat 10:40,42\f*  
\v 11 It…®mat ekotolkeike m…ôm…ô it…ômat rafin nakoat…ôk…ôike katos nolkeike…ôn it…ôm n…ôkoatol, moatol m…ôm…ô otatuw…®n e namnun, k…ôn it…ômat nakotos nat un it…ôm nakotag…®le lan.\f + \fr 6:11 \ft Hip 3:6\f*  
\v 12 It…®mat esotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô nakot…ôlpah, m…ôto ekotolkeike m…ôm…ô on…ôkotos nol…ôn\f + \fr 6:12 \ft Hip 13:7\f* r…ôha net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm kotaiu aup…ôn. Ilat kotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n k…ôn moatol r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn kaif…ôm…ôh.\f + \fr 6:12 \ft Jem 1:3; Nol ∆èp…ôn 13:10; 14:12\f* Moatol n…ôhlan, k…ôn roiu, ilat k…®notos r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat.\f + \fr 6:12 \ft Hip 10:36\f*   
\s1 R…ôhatat iagke t…ôtat…®g e nego e neai  
\p
\v 13 N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kit tol n…ôhlan, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn k…ôm Epraham aup…ôn. Nian Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôhan, k…ôn n…ôr…®g kit t…®k…ô m…®n m…ôm…ô in otos mol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn lan r…ôhan t…ôf…®g…ôm. M…ôto-inu n…ôrg…®n in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôrg…®n m…®n rafin. Tol n…ôhlan, Uhg…®n t…ômos noanaw…®l at…®p …ôm e n…ôrg…®n, mat…ôn m…ôm…ô,\f + \fr 6:13 \ft Jen 22:16\f*  
\v 14 ‚ÄúIo oek…ôhlman r…ôhak n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm ik, iahgin. Io oekol r…ôham noanol otuwa tep…ôt tepet.‚Äù\f + \fr 6:14 \ft Jen 22:17\f*  
\v 15 M…ôto-inu Epraham r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôf…ôm…ôh, in t…ômat…ôsahgin matuw…®n matuw…®n, m…ôtoarus nian in t…ômos nat…®mnat m…®n un it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm in.\f + \fr 6:15 \ft Jen 21:5\f*   
\p
\v 16 Nian et…ômim tatos noanaw…®l e n…ôrg…® et…ôm-iasol kit r…ôhan,\f + \fr 6:16 \ft E nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôlis…ôn n…ôghat…ôn t…ôskas…®k, ok…ôm…ô kitat kit tolkeike m…ôm…ô otol n…ôhlan, k…ôn in tatos noanaw…®l e man…®n ne w…®n…®n ne. M…ôto net…ôm Isrel aup…ôn, ilat k…ômoatos noanaw…®l e n…ôrg…® et…ôm asim kit, o nat kit it…ôm tasim, k…ôn nian net…ômim neen koat…ôto, k…ôn ilat koatahat…ôt…ô e n…ôghat…ôn it…ôm koat…ôn. Okol k…ôsot…ôrg…ôh…ôu m…®n…ôn ron, m…ôto-inu n…ôr…®g …ôh k…ômot…ôn, in tat…ôlis …ôtain n…ôghat…ôn, t…ôskas…®k.\f* k…ôn noanaw…®l u r…ôhan, tat…ôlis r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn t…ôf…®g…ôm. K…ôn net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike motahat…ôt…ô e r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn, okol k…ôsot…ôrg…ôh…ôu m…®n…ôn ron.\f + \fr 6:16 \ft Eks 22:11\f*  
\v 17 Uhg…®n t…ômos noanaw…®l e n…ôrg…®n n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu in tolkeike m…ôm…ô otol net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm okotos nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm in t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s,\f + \fr 6:17 \ft Rom 4:16\f* ilat okot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô r…ôhan nalp…ôkau…ôn, okol t…ôs…ôuhlin…ôn nian kit.\f + \fr 6:17 \ft Nam 23:19; Taet 1:2\f*  
\v 18 Uhg…®n tatos noanaw…®l n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhatat u, it…ôm k…®notiet r…ôk…®s motag…®m k…ôn moatahg…®l-p…ôn lan. K…ôn p…ôs kitat kotask…ôl…®m-i…ôk…®s nol…ôn …ôh it…ôm Uhg…®n t…®nos-ipa r…ôk…®s k…ôm itat, m…ôm…ô kitat okotag…®le …ôskas…®k e n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn m…®n r…ôhan. Nat mil u, ilau okol k…ôsu…ôuhlin…ôn nian kit, m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n, t…ôseiu…ô…ôn nian kit.  
\v 19 Kitat kot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhatat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôskas…®k o nos…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, tol n…ôhlan, mol m…ôm…ô in tahmen e iagke kit it…ôm t…ôtask…ôl…®m w…®r r…ôhatat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn,\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Fil 3:12\f* m…ôm…ô nat kit ot…ôs…ôloal…ôn lan k…ôn m…ôsiuw r…ôk…®s m…®n…ôn kitat. Tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô iagke u, in t…®nat…®g r…ôk…®s …ôp…ôh im…ô e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n, …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai, e n…ôwtain n…®m…ôhan im…ô-p…ôn ik…®n.\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Lev 16:2; Hip 9:2,3,7\f*  
\v 20 Ik…®n …ôh, Iesu t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s ik…®n r…ôhatat lan, m…ôm…ô oter…ôh e suat…®p r…ôhatat.\f + \fr 6:20 \ft Hip 4:14\f* In t…ômuwa r…ôk…®s pris asol ag…®n\f + \fr 6:20 \ft Hip 2:17\f* tahmen …ôm e pris u Melkisetek\f + \fr 6:20 \ft Hip 5:16\f* aup…ôn, k…ôn in otatos w…ôk u nian rafin, namnun t…®k…ô.   
\c 7  
\s1 Melkisetek,  //  Kig r…ôha N…ôtuat…®p…ôn,  //  Kig r…ôha N…ôm…ôlinu…ôn,  //  ne pris r…ôha Uhg…®n Il…®s Ag…®n  
\m
\v 1 Suah u, Melkisetek,\f + \fr 7:1 \ft Jen 14:17-20\f* in kig r…ôha Salem\f + \fr 7:1 \ft N…ôrg…®n …ôh, Salem, in n…ôrg…®n oas r…ôha Jerusalem aup…ôn. N…ôrg…®n …ôh, Salem, n…®p…ôt…®n u ‚Äún…ôm…ôlinu…ôn.‚Äù\f*, k…ôn in pris r…ôha Uhg…®n u Il…®s P…®k Ag…®n. Aup…ôn, nian Epraham t…ômuw…®n e n…ôluag…®n…ôn ilat kig m…®n, k…ôn in t…ômol win elat. K…ôn in m…®n…®t…ôl…®g m…®natuwa. Melkisetek, in t…ômatuw…®n m…ôplan Epraham e suat…®p, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôfak m…ôtap…ôhin-p…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm Epraham.  
\v 2 K…ôn Epraham, t…ômos-ir…ôk…®s tait e r…ôhan nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm t…ômol win lan e n…ôluag…®n…ôn, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn k…ôm Melkisetek. Melkisetek u, n…®p…ôt…® n…ôrg…®n un, ‚ÄúKig r…ôha N…ôtuat…®p…ôn.‚Äù K…ôn n…ôrg…®n kit m…®n u, k…ôtaun-in m…ôm…ô Kig r…ôha Salem, n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúKig r…ôha N…ôm…ôlinu…ôn.‚Äù  
\v 3 Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôs…ôghat-in…ôn r…ôhan tata ne mama ne r…ôhan noanol m…®n. K…ôn t…ôs…ôn…ôn nian t…ômaiir lan, ne nian it…ôm t…ôm…®m…®s lan. Tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô in t…ôm…ôs…®m…®s…ôn, in tatol …ôh w…ôk r…ôha pris. Tol n…ôhlan, n…ôk…ôplan m…ôm…ô in tahmen e N…ôt…® Uhg…®n u, in pris lil…®n kit\f + \fr 7:3 \ft Sam 110:4\f*   
\p
\v 4 N…®kim tu…ôh-tu Melkisetek. In et…ôm-iasol kit. Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô t…®p…®tat u Epraham in et…ôm-iasol, m…ôto in t…ômat…®siai-in p…®k Melkisetek, matos-ip…ôn r…ôhan nat asol m…®n …ôm, in …ôm in …ôm, m…ôm…ô r…ôhan tait k…ôm in.\f + \fr 7:4 \ft Jen 14:20\f*  
\v 5 Kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô, e nup m…®n rafin, net…ôm Isrel ilat kot…ôk…ôike moatos-ip…ôn r…ôhalat tait k…ôm noanol m…®n r…ôha Lifae, ilat u pris m…®n, tahmen-p…ôn …ôm m…ôm…ô inu Lou r…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn mihin. Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô pris m…®n …ôh, ilat noanol m…®n r…ôha Epraham, m…ôto net…ôm im…ôlat ik…®n ilat kot…ôk…ôike moatos-ip…ôn tait k…ôm ilat.  
\v 6 Melkisetek u, in s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol kit r…ôha Lifae. M…ôto in t…ômos tait m…®n u r…ôha nat…®mnat r…ôha Epraham. K…ôn in t…ôm…ôfak-p…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôhan\f + \fr 7:6 \ft Jen 14:19,20\f* k…ôm Epraham u, Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn r…ôhan n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn k…ôm in.  
\v 7 K…ôn t…ôtuat…®p ag…®n m…ôm…ô et…ômim it…ôm tatos n…ôr…®g asol ot…ôfak m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn tatuw…®n e et…ômim it…ôm l…ôhau …ôm lan.  
\v 8 K…ôn pris m…®n u it…ôm koatos tait u, ilat net…ômim …ôm, it…ôm ok…ôpanot…®m…®s. M…ôto Melkisetek u, in tatos tait, kat…ôn m…ôm…ô in tat…ômeg…ôh.\f + \fr 7:8 \ft Hip 5:6\f*  
\v 9 Epraham t…ômat…ôtou r…ôhan tait tatuw…®n k…ôm Melkisetek nulan, k…ôn k…®tun n…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô Lifae u, et…ôm tatos tait r…ôha net…ôm Isrel, in m…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn tait k…ôm Melkisetek.  
\v 10 M…ôto-inu nian Melkisetek t…ôm…ôplan Epraham, Lifae t…ôm…ôsaiir…ôn …ôh. M…ôto nian Epraham t…ôm…ôtou nulan tait tuw…®n k…ôm Melkisetek, in tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô r…ôhan u noanol, Lifae, in m…®n t…ôm…ôtou-p…ôn tait k…ôm Melkisetek, m…ôto-inun in t…®n…ôtat…®g r…ôk…®s e n…®p…ôt…® r…ôhan pipi.\f + \fr 7:10 \ft Nat k…®s…®l k…ôt…ôhal…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô Melkisetek in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in pris m…®n u noanol r…ôha Lifae. Kiti…ôh un, Melkisetek in t…ôm…ôs…®m…®s…ôn, tat…ômeg…ôh …ôh. K…ôiu un, t…®p…® Lifae u Epraham, in t…ômatos-ip…ôn tait r…ôhan k…ôm Melkisetek. K…®s…®l un, Melkisetek t…ôm…ôfak-p…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô ot…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm Epraham, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô Epraham t…ôm…ôfak o Melkisetek.\f*   
\s1 Kristo in tahmen e Melkisetek  
\p
\v 11 W…ôk r…ôha pris m…®n u, k…ômot…®s…®-p…ôn e noanol r…ôha Lifae, in n…ôuk…ôt…® Lou it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ôm Isrel. M…ôto w…ôk r…ôha pris m…®n u, in t…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn mahmen.\f + \fr 7:11 \ft Hip 7:18,19; 8:7\f* M…ôto-inu pris m…®n u, ilat k…ôsotahmen…ôn. Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô ilat k…ôsotahmen…ôn nian in t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr pris kit m…®n tuwa.\f + \fr 7:11 \ft Hip 10:1\f* K…ôn pris un in t…ôruru n…®s…®-p…ôn…ôn e noanol r…ôha Lifae ne Eron,\f + \fr 7:11 \ft Lifae in noanol r…ôha pris m…®n, m…ôto Eron in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e noanol r…ôha Lifae, k…ôn noanol m…®n r…ôhan, kat…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat pris asol ag…®n m…®n.\f* m…ôto in pris kit tahmen e Melkisetek.  
\v 12 Nian k…ôm…ôuhlin nol…ôn r…ôha n…®t…ôpun…ôn pris, k…ôn ok…ôike k…ôuhlin m…®n Lou.  
\v 13 Ot…ôk…ôike mol nulan m…ôto-inun, kitat koat…ôt…ôghat-in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat, it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e noanol kit it…ôm s…ôn…ôm…ô noanol …ôtuat…®p r…ôha pris m…®n, it…ôm koatol w…ôk e olta.  
\v 14 K…®tat k…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat in t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e noanol r…ôha Juta,\f + \fr 7:14 \ft Jen 49:10; Mat 1:3; 2:6; Nol ∆èp…ôn 5:5\f* k…ôn nian Lou r…ôha Moses t…ômat…ôghat-in w…ôk r…ôha pris m…®n, in t…ôm…ôs…ôghat-in ag…®n-…ôh…ôn noanol u.  
\v 15 M…ôto t…ôw…®r …ôm, m…ôto-inu kitat k…®not…®tun m…ôm…ô pris kit m…®n t…®n…ômuwa r…ôk…®s, it…ôm tahmen e Melkisetek.  
\v 16 In t…ômuwa pris, m…ôto s…ôn…ôm…ô Lou t…ômol mak e noanol r…ôhan m…ôm…ô noanol u in r…ôha pris m…®n. In t…ômos w…ôk r…ôha pris e nat kit it…ôm t…ôsan…ôn mapr…ôk…®s-in Lou, inu n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn u r…ôhan it…ôm namnun t…®k…ô.\f + \fr 7:16 \ft Jon 1:4; 5:26; Hip 7:25\f*  
\v 17 Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIk pris kit tahmen e Melkisetek\f + \fr 7:17 \ft Jen 14:18; Sam 110:4; Sek 6:13; Hip 5:6,10; 6:20; 7:1-22\f* aup…ôn,  
\q1 k…ôn ik onakatol w…ôk r…ôha pris nian rafin,  
\q1 matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô.‚Äù   
\p
\v 18 K…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu kal…®n Lou aup…ôn, m…ôto-inun r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn t…®k…ô, in t…ôsasitu…ôn, okol t…ôsol…ôn nat kit.\f + \fr 7:18 \ft Rom 8:3; Kal 3:21; Hip 9:9; 10:1\f*  
\v 19 M…ôto-inu Lou …ôh, t…ôruru n…ôl…ôh…ôu …ôtuat…®p…ôn nat kit.\f + \fr 7:19 \ft Rom 3:20\f* K…ôn roiu …ôh, nol…ôn p…®s…®n kit it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s, in t…®nos n…ômeen, m…ôm…ô kitat okot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhatat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn lan. K…ôn in suat…®p r…ôhatat u, o nuw…®n…ôn iu…ôhk…®r o Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 7:19 \ft Hip 4:16; 10:22; Jem 4:8\f*   
\p
\v 20 Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô Kristo in otol w…ôk r…ôha pris matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô, k…ôn t…ômos noanaw…®l ron, m…ôm…ô r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn ot…ôf…®g…ôm. M…ôto t…ôm…ôsos…ôn noanaw…®l mihin e pris m…®n aup…ôn.  
\v 21 M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômos …ôm noanaw…®l nian Iesu t…ômuwa pris. Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ômos noanaw…®l kit,  
\q1 k…ôn okol k…ôs…ôuhlin…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhan.\f + \fr 7:21 \ft 1 Saml 15:29; Mal 3:6\f*  
\q1 In tat…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòIk on…ôkol w…ôk r…ôha pris nian rafin,\f + \fr 7:21 \ft Sam 110:4; Hip 5:6; 6:20; 7:17\f*  
\q1 matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô.‚Äô‚Äù   
\m
\v 22 Uhg…®n t…ômos noanaw…®l n…ôhlan, matol m…ô Iesu tuwa mol suat…®p it…ôm tatol kitat kot…®tun …ôsas m…ôm…ô n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn in t…ôw…®r, mapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn u aup…ôn.\f + \fr 7:22 \ft Luk 22:20; Hip 8:6; 12:24\f*   
\p
\v 23 Aup…ôn, pris m…®n ilat tep…ôt, m…ôto-inun kiti…ôh tol w…ôk matuw…®n matuw…®n m…®m…®s un, kit tos n…ômeen, mol w…ôk matuw…®n matuw…®n, m…®m…®s moatol …ôm nulan. Ilat k…ôsotol…ôn w…ôk lil…®n.  
\v 24 M…ôto Iesu, in otos w…ôk r…ôha pris r…ôhatat matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô, m…ôto-inun, t…ôtat…®g lil…®n.  
\v 25 Tol n…ôhlan, in t…®tun nosmeg…ôh lil…®n…ôn\f + \fr 7:25 \ft Suat…®p kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n o n…ôn…ôn, m…ôm…ô, ‚Äút…®tun nosmeg…ôh ag…®n-…ôh…ôn.‚Äù\f* kitat u, kot…®lp…®n kitat min m…ôm…ô koatuw…®n o Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu in tat…ômeg…ôh lil…®n, tat…ôghat r…ôhatat lan k…ôm Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 7:25 \ft Rom 8:34; 1 Jon 2:1\f*   
\p
\v 26 O nat u, inun in pris asol ag…®n\f + \fr 7:26 \ft Hip 2:17; 4:14; 6:20; 8:1\f* it…ôm in tahmen o nasitu…ôn etat. In tasim, k…ôn m…ôtuat…®p w…®r, in t…ôsol…ôn nol…ôn rat. In tol p…®s…®n ag…®n e net…ôm koatol t…ôfag…ô rat, k…ôn in il…®s tapr…ôk…®s-in ilat …ôp…ôh e nego e neai.  
\v 27 In tol p…®s…®n e pris asol ag…®n m…®n un aup…ôn. Nian rafin, ilat kot…ôk…ôike kaup…ôn moatol sakrifais o naf…ôl r…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôhalat.\f + \fr 7:27 \ft Lev 9:8; 16:6,\f* Uaris…®g lan un, ilat k…ôpanotol m…®n sakrifais kit m…®n, o naf…ôl r…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôha net…ômim m…®n.\f + \fr 7:27 \ft Lev 9:15; 16:15; Hip 5:1,3\f* M…ôto nian Iesu tateg…ôhan-in m…ôm…ô in otol sakrifais at…®p e r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn,\f + \fr 7:27 \ft Efes 5:2\f* k…ôn mau kiti…ôh …ôm\f + \fr 7:27 \ft Rom 6:10; Hip 9:12, 26,28; 10:10; 1 Pita 3:18\f* in tahmen moau.  
\v 28 Lou in tat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr pris m…®n it…ôm k…ôsotahmen…ôn.\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Hip 5:1-2\f* M…ôto noanaw…®l r…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm tatuaris…®g-in Lou, in tat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr N…ôt…®n u,\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Hip 1:2\f* it…ôm t…ôw…®r mahmen ag…®n\f + \fr 7:28 \ft Hip 2:10\f* o nol…ôn w…ôk u, matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô.   
\c 8  
\s1 Iesu in pris asol ag…®n t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s-in net…ôm m…®n un k…ômotol w…ôk r…ôha pris asol ag…®n aup…ôn  
\m
\v 1 Kitat koat…ôghat-in nat u,\f + \fr 8:1 \ft Hip 1:3; 2:17; 3:1; 4:14; 6:20; 7:26; 9:11; 10:12; 12:2\f* m…ôto n…ôuk…ôt…®n tol nulan. Kitat koatos pris asol ag…®n kit, t…ôtuat…®p …ôm e it…ôm un emat…ôn. In t…®nat…ôp…ôl…ôh r…ôk…®s\f + \fr 8:1 \ft ∆èplan-tu futnot e 1:3\f* e r…ôhn mat…®p Et…ôm-iasol …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai, ik…®n r…ôha nep…ôt…ôn ne n…®siaii…ôn.  
\v 2 In tatol w…ôk …ôp…ôh Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n e nego e neai, inu Nim…ô Tapol…ôn pahrien\f + \fr 8:2 \ft Hip 3:6; 10:21; 1 Pita 2:5; Nol ∆èp…ôn 13:6\f* it…ôm Uhg…®n …ôm t…ômiuw. S…ôn…ôm…ô et…ômim it…ôm t…ômiuw Nim…ô Tapol…ôn …ôh.\f + \fr 8:2 \ft Hip 9:11, 24\f*   
\p
\v 3 K…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr rafin pris asol ag…®n m…®n u aup…ôn, m…ôm…ô okoatos-ip…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôn moatol sakrifais. E suat…®p kiti…ôh …ôm, r…ôhatat u pris asol ag…®n, in m…®n ot…ôk…ôike mos-ip…ôn sakrifais kit k…ôm Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 8:3 \ft Hip 9:14\f*  
\v 4 Ok…ôm…ô in t…ôtat…®g …ôh e n…ôtueint…ôn u, k…ôn okol s…ôn…ôm…ô in pris kit, m…ôto-inu pris m…®n …ôp…ôh ik…®n koatat…®g it…ôm koatos-ip…ôn nat…®mnat k…ôm Uhg…®n, tahmen …ôm m…ô inu Lou t…ôm…ôn mihin.  
\v 5 Pris m…®n u, ilat koatol r…ôhalat w…ôk e narm…® nim…ô …ôm it…ôm tatasg…ôw…®n\f + \fr 8:5 \ft Kol 2:17; Hip 9:23\f* nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm t…ôtat…®g e nego e neai. Tol n…ôhlan, nian Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Moses aup…ôn, m…ôm…ô otiuw Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim, in t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOnak…ôk…ôike matehm w…®r m…ôm…ô on…ôkol nat…®mnat m…®n u t…ôtuat…®p tahmen …ôm e r…ôhak mak it…ôm emol mat…ôg…ôtun r…ôk…®s ik lan …ôp…ôh il…®s e n…®tot asol.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:5 \ft Eks 25:40\f*  
\v 6 M…ôto roiu, Iesu, pris asol ag…®n u r…ôhatat, in t…®nos r…ôhan w…ôk it…ôm t…ôw…®r t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s-in w…ôk r…ôhalat. K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, Iesu in suat…®p r…ôha n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi r…ôha nasitu…ôn u, in t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s-in n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn oas r…ôha nasitu…ôn. M…ôto-inu n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi u, in tat…ôtul-p…ôr e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm kot…ôw…®r motapr…ôk…®s.\f + \fr 8:6 \ft Hip 8:8,13; Luk 22:20; Hip 7:22; 9:15; 12:24\f*   
\p
\v 7 M…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô k…ôsehm…ôn nat t…ôrat kit e n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn oas,\f + \fr 8:7 \ft Hip 7:11,18; 10:1\f* okol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi t…ôsos…ôn n…ômeen.  
\v 8 M…ôto Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôplan n…ôrat…ôn r…ôha net…ômim, k…ôn t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúNian …ôh-ik…®n ot…ôpanuwa,  
\q1 it…ôm io, oekol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi r…ôha nasitu…ôn r…ôha noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ne noanol m…®n r…ôha Juta.   
\q1
\v 9 N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn u,  
\q1 in otol p…®s…®n ag…®n e n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn oas r…ôha nasitu…ôn,  
\q1 it…ôm io emol k…ôm t…®p…®lat m…®n aup…ôn,  
\q1 e nian u it…ôm io emos nelm…®lat matit ilat moatiet r…ôk…®s Ijip.  
\q1 Oiakol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi r…ôha nasitu…ôn,  
\q1 m…ôto-inu ilat k…ôm…ôsotask…ôl…®m…ôn n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn u it…ôm io emol k…ôm ilat aup…ôn,  
\q1 k…ôn tol m…ôm…ô io emap…ôs ilat, maluin.\f + \fr 8:9 \ft Eks 19:5-6\f*   
\q1
\v 10 K…ôn io, I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, iat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 e nian it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa,  
\q1 io oekol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi kit r…ôha nasitu…ôn\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Rom 11:27\f* k…ôm noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel.  
\q1 Oekos-ip…ôn r…ôhak lou m…®n e r…ôhalat-kap…ô,  
\q1 k…ôn oek…ôte r…ôk…®s-p…ôn e n…®kilat,\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Lou oas m…®n u, k…ôm…ôte-p…ôn e k…ôpiel k…ôiu kuepin-epin. 2 Kor. 3:3; Hip 10:16\f*  
\q1 k…ôn io ekuwa mol Uhg…®n …ôtuat…®p r…ôhalat,  
\q1 k…ôn ilat okotuwa kol r…ôhak …ôtuat…®p net…ômim.\f + \fr 8:10 \ft Esik 11:20\f*   
\q1
\v 11 Ilat kit okol t…ôsuw…®n…ôn m…ôg…ôtun net…ôm iman ik…®n m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄòIk onak…ôk…ôike m…®tun I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô u.‚Äô  
\q1 K…ôn et…ômim kit okol t…ôsuw…®n…ôn m…ôn-ip…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u k…ôm pian,  
\q1 m…ôto-inun ilat rafin okot…®tun io,\f + \fr 8:11 \ft Aes 11:9; Jon 6:45\f*  
\q1 t…ôtuoun e net…ôm …ôpnap…®n m…®n  
\q1 muw…®n m…ôtoarus-p…ôn net…ôm koatos n…ôr…®g asol m…®n.   
\q1
\v 12 M…ôto-inun, io, ekas…ôkitun ilat o r…ôhalat nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm t…ôs…ôtuat…®p ag…®n-…ôh…ôn.  
\q1 Io oekaf…ôl r…ôk…®s nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat,  
\q1 k…ôn io oekaluin nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:12 \ft Aes 43:25; 64:9; Maeka 7:19; Hip 10:17; Jer 31:31-34\f* \f + \fr 8:12 \ft Hip 10:16\f*   
\p
\v 13 Nian Uhg…®n tat…ôghat-in n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn u, m…ôm…ô in n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi, n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn aup…ôn, t…®noas m…®n…ôrat. K…ôn nat it…ôm in t…®nuwa m…®noas, t…®n…ôsahmen m…®n…ôn, k…ôn ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, t…®k…ô.   
\c 9  
\s1 Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn ne Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n e nego e neai  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn e n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn mat…®g, ilat okot…ôike mot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p …ôtuat…®p m…®n o n…ôfak…ôn. K…ôn Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim, in r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm u.\fig Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim|alt="tabernacle" src="LB00259B.TIF" size="span" loc="Heb 9:1-2" ref="9:1" \fig*  
\v 2 Net…ôm aup…ôn, k…ômotiuw Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim u,\f + \fr 9:2 \ft Eks 25:8,9\f* moatol noan kit …ôp…ôh ilug…®n …ôtuat…®p, k…ômag…ôhl noan k…ôiu. Noan it…ôm t…ôtaup…ôn lan, koat…ôn m…ôm…ô Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n.\f + \fr 9:2 \ft Eks 26:33,34\f* E noan …ôh, k…ômot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nat kat…ôhtu-p…ôr lait lan\f + \fr 9:2 \ft Eks 25:31-40; Jon 8:12; Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:20\f* ik…®n, ne tep…®l kit it…ôm k…ôm…ôl…®n-p…ôr p…®ret asim m…®n lan.\f + \fr 9:2 \ft Eks 25:23-29; Jon 6:35,48\f*\fig Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n|alt="interior of tabernacle" src="BK00278B.TIF" size="span" loc="Heb 9:2" ref="9:2" \fig*  
\v 3 K…ômiuwos…®g n…®m…ôhan e noan uaris…®g, k…ôn noan …ôh, kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIk…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:3 \ft Eks 26:31-33\f*  
\v 4 Ik…®n …ôh, nat kit …ôh-ik…®n k…ômol e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, it…ôm kat…ômki-p…ôn nat pien-pien lan, katuwaan. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, Bok…®s r…ôha N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn R…ôha Nasitu…ôn\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Bok…®s r…ôha N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn R…ôha Nasitu…ôn u, in ‚ÄúCovenant Box.‚Äù Eks 25:10-22\f* tat…ôp…ôl…ôh …ôh-ik…®n. Bok…®s u, k…ômol e n…®g, k…ôn kalpin e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t. K…ôn e n…®p…ôgnoa Bok…®s …ôh, p…ôt…ôl kit …ôh-ik…®n k…ômol e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, k…ômar…®gin-p…ôn p…®ret u mana,\f + \fr 9:4 \ft E nian r…ôha Moses, Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn p…®ret t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e neai, n…ôrg…®n u mana. Eks 16:31-33; Jon 6:48-51.\f* noan m…ôs…®n ik…®n. K…ônu k…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn m…®n kas…®k…®n r…ôha Eron e Bok…®s u, kas…®k…®n it…ôm aup…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômol t…ôwi…ô m…®n.\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Nam 17:1-10\f* K…ôn k…ôpiel mil k…ôiu …ôh-ik…®n, it…ôm kuepin-epin, k…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s-p…ôn Lou ilat ten elau.\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Eks 31:18\f*\fig Bok…®s R…ôha N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn R…ôha Nasitu…ôn|alt="ark of the covenant (Melody Carlson)" src="ark2b&w.tif" size="col" loc="Heb 9:4-5" ref="9:4" \fig*  
\v 5 K…ôn il…®s e r…ôhn-m…®nat Bok…®s u, narm…® Jerubim r…ôha N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn,\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Jerubim inu, kat…ôn m…ôm…ô Jerubim r…ôha N…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn, m…ôto-inun n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn asol r…ôha n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g ilug…®n elau. Nian neen ilau katioas n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôtian …ôh kit (Esik 1:4-21; 10:9-22; Sam 18:10).\f* ilau k…ôiu …ôh-ik…®n. K…ôtiauwos…®g n…®m…ôlm…ôl…®lau o Ik…®n Kat…®lp…®n Nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n Ik…®n.\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Ik…®n Kat…®lp…®n Nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n Ik…®n, inun, r…ôhn-m…®nat Bok…®s r…ôha N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn il…®s ik…®n. Ik…®n …ôh, n…ôhag-…ôhag…ôn asol r…ôha n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g ik…®n. Net…ômim kot…ôruru nuw…®n…ôn im…ô Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôto pris asol ag…®n …ôm. K…ôn in t…ôsuw…®n…ôn nian rafin. Nian kiti…ôh …ôm e nup kiti…ôh tatuw…®n. Pris asol ag…®n t…®tun nuw…®n…ôn im…ô Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n, in t…ôm…®k n…®ta r…ôha sakrifais k…ôn muw…®n k…ôn t…ômorautin n…®ta e r…ôhn-m…®nat bok…®s u. Nol…ôn …ôh, in n…ômt…ôtin w…®r kit, it…ôm tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike k…®m…®s o r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat m…®n. M…ôto e n…®ta …ôh r…ôha sakrifais, in tat…®lp…®n nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f* \f + \fr 9:5 \ft Eks 25:17-22; Hip 4:16\f* M…ôto okol es…ôn…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôte …ôlk…ôl…ôh, p…ôs ek…ôl…ôh…ôu …ôm e s…ôpag.   
\p
\v 6 Nian k…ômot…ôl…®n w…®r rafin nat…®mnat m…®n u, pris m…®n kot…®tun nuw…®n…ôn im…ô miet e noan it…ôm t…ôtaup…ôn nian ilat koatol w…ôk r…ôha n…ôfak…ôn.\f + \fr 9:6 \ft Nam 28:2-4\f*  
\v 7 M…ôto pris asol ag…®n, in …ôm t…®tun nuw…®n…ôn im…ô e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n. M…ôto okol t…ôsuw…®n…ôn nian rafin.\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Lev 16:2\f* In t…®tun nuw…®n…ôn nian kiti…ôh …ôm e nup m…®n rafin.\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Lev 16:34\f* K…ôn nian in tatuw…®n, in t…ôike mos n…®ta, k…ôn mol sakrifais lan o nol…ôn rat r…ôhan,\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Lev 16:3,11,14; Hip 5:3\f* k…ôn mat…®g mol m…®n o nol…ôn rat r…ôha net…ômim,\f + \fr 9:7 \ft Lev 16:15\f* it…ôm ilat kot…ôruru m…ôm…ô koatol t…ôfag…ô rat.\fig Pris Asol Ag…®n|alt="priest with blood in bowl" src="HK00273B.TIF" size="col" loc="Heb 9:7" ref="9:7" \fig*  
\v 8 K…ôn e nat…®mnat m…®n u, Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô, nian Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim aup…ôn t…ômat…ôtul …ôh, k…ôn suat…®p\f + \fr 9:8 \ft Luk 23:45; Jon 14:6; Hip 10:19-20\f* t…®k…ô o kitat o nuw…®n…ôn e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n.  
\v 9 (In tahmen …ôm e narm…® nat kit\f + \fr 9:9 \ft Hip 10:1-2\f* it…ôm tat…ôg…ôtun e nian u it…ôm kotat…®g lan roiu.) Nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm pris m…®n koatos-ip…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n, moatol sakrifais lan k…ôm in,\f + \fr 9:9 \ft Hip 5:1; 8:3\f* nat…®mnat m…®n u, k…ôsotahmen…ôn o n…ôl…ôh…ôu …ôtuat…®p…ôn n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ômim it…ôm kotuwa o n…ôfak…ôn.  
\v 10 M…ôto-inu n…ôfak…ôn oas aup…ôn, in tat…ôg…ôtun …ôm suat…®p m…®n it…ôm koat…ôn p…®k nol…ôn r…ôha nagw…ôn…ôn\f + \fr 9:10 \ft Lev 11:2-23\f* ne n…ôn…®m…ôn\f + \fr 9:10 \ft Nam 6:3; Kolosi 2:16\f* ne naikuas…ôn.\f + \fr 9:10 \ft Lev 11:25,28,40\f* Nat…®mnat m…®n u, in nat r…ôha n…®p…ôt…®t…ôm …ôm. M…ôto nol…ôn m…®n …ôh, ilat katipa …ôf…®g…ôm …ôm kit r…ôha net…ômim, matuw…®n m…ôtoarus-p…ôn nian Uhg…®n ot…ôuhlin nat…®mnat rafin tuwa muwiwi.   
\s1 N…®ta Iesu in sakrifais kit it…ôm in t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s ag…®n-…ôh  
\p
\v 11 M…ôto roiu …ôh, Kristo t…®nuwa r…ôk…®s, k…ôn in pris asol ag…®n it…ôm t…ôm…ôm…®k nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n, m…®nuwa.\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Hip 10:1\f* K…ôn in t…ômuw…®n im…ô e Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim it…ôm t…ôw…®r t…ôhm…®n m…®n, mapr…ôk…®s-in it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn.\f + \fr 9:11 \ft Hip 8:2; 9:24\f* Nim…ô …ôh, in s…ôn…ôm…ô nat kit it…ôm net…ômim k…ômotol, k…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô nat kit r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol.  
\v 12 Nian Kristo t…ômuw…®n im…ô e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n, t…ôm…ôsuw…®n…ôn e nup m…®n rafin, tahmen e pris asol ag…®n m…®n aup…ôn k…ômotol mihin. In t…ômol mau kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn tahmen, m…ôto-inun in t…ôsos…ôn n…®ta n…ôni ne n…®ta n…ôt…® kau muw…®n im…ô m…ôm…ô otos-ir…ôk…®s t…ôfag…ô rat. K…ôp…ô, in t…ômos at…®p …ôm n…®tan, muw…®n im…ô, k…ôn in …ôm t…ôm…ôtou n…ômt…®tat m…®k…®s itat e t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n.\f + \fr 9:12 \ft Rom 3:25\f*  
\v 13 E nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn aup…ôn, k…ômorautin-p…ôn n…®ta n…ôni ne kau, o n…ômtapi kau it…ôm k…ômuwaan …ôt…®p e olta, korautin-p…ôn e suah kit it…ôm tamk…®m…®k e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô n…®p…ôt…®n otaru…ôtu…ôh, namk…®m…®k…ôn t…®k…ô lan.  
\v 14 M…ôto n…®ta Iesu\f + \fr 9:14 \ft 1 Pita 1:2,18-19\f* in tatos n…ôsan…ôn…ôn asol tapr…ôk…®s-in nat…®mnat m…®n u.\f + \fr 9:14 \ft Hip 10:4\f* Kristo in t…ômol at…®p sakrifais lan, e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n it…ôm t…ôtat…®g lil…®n. In sakrifais kit it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p ag…®n, n…ôrat…ôn kit t…®k…ô lan. Tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn n…®tan in tatos n…ôsan…ôn…ôn, tahmen o naf…ôl…ôn n…®kit…ômat\f + \fr 9:14 \ft Sek 13:1; Hip 10:2,22; 1 Jon 1:7\f* o nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm kot…®tun nit-ip…ôn…ôn it…ôm e n…®m…®s…ôn, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkot…ôfak …ôm k…ôm Uhg…®n it…ôm tat…ômeg…ôh.\f + \fr 9:14 \ft Taet 2:14\f*   
\p
\v 15 O nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm Iesu t…ômol, in suat…®p o nos…ôn n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi r…ôha nasitu…ôn.\f + \fr 9:15 \ft Luk 22:20\f* Uhg…®n t…ômaun-in net…ômim r…ôhan, k…ôn m…ôn-i…ôk…®s k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n u, in r…ôhalat. K…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u, okol k…ôsot…®k…ô…ôn nian kit,\f + \fr 9:15 \ft Hip 10:34\f* m…ôto okoatat…®g lil…®n. Ilat okotos nat…®mnat m…®n un, m…ôto-inun n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôha Kristo in t…®n…ôtou r…ôk…®s n…ômt…® t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôha net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm k…ômoat…ôtg…ôhl Lou r…ôha n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn mat…®g.   
\p
\v 16 Ok…ôm…ô Iesus t…ôs…®m…®s…ôn n…ôhlan, k…ôn r…ôhan net…ômim ok…ôsotos…ôn nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n it…ôm in t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ô r…ôhalat. M…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô suah kit tol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kit m…ôm…ô nian in ot…®m…®s, k…ôn r…ôhan nat…®mnat otuw…®n o suah p…®s…®n kit, k…ôn suah u in ot…ôk…ôike m…®m…®s pit…ôn, k…ônu n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôhan in ot…ôtat…®g mat…ômeg…ôh.  
\v 17 N…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kit tol n…ôhlan, t…ôsat…®g…ôn m…ôs…ômeg…ôh…ôn nian et…ôm t…ôm…ôn t…ôtat…®g …ôh. R…ôhan n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn in ot…ôtat…®g mat…ômeg…ôh …ôm nian in t…®n…®m…®s r…ôk…®s.  
\v 18 O nat…®mnat m…®n u, e n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn aup…ôn, n…®ta nat meg…ôh kit t…ôike mai…ôh, t…ôg…ôtun m…ôm…ô nat kit t…ôm…®m…®s, k…ôn otol m…ôm…ô n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn in tat…ômeg…ôh m…ôtat…®g.  
\v 19 Tol n…ôhlan, nian Moses in t…ômat…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôk…®s n…ôghat…ôn m…®n rafin r…ôha Lou k…ôm net…ômim, k…ôn uaris…®g lan, in t…ômos n…®m…ôme sipsip k…ômol tasi…ô, ne nelm…® n…®g u hisop, meer-p…ôn e n…®ta n…ôt…® kau ne n…®ta n…ôni ne n…ôhau, k…ôn t…ômorautin-p…ôn n…®ta e naoa r…ôha Lou ne net…ômim m…®n.\f + \fr 9:19 \ft Eks 24:6-8\f*  
\v 20 K…ôn in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúInu n…®ta nat meg…ôh kit it…ôm tat…®m…®s o nol…ôn n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g mat…ômeg…ôh. K…ôn it…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike moat…®siai-in, moatol n…ôwian.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:20 \ft Eks 24:8; Luk 22:20\f*  
\v 21 E nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, Moses t…ômorautin-p…ôn n…®ta e Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim ne nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm k…ômos o n…ôfak…ôn.  
\v 22 Lou tat…ôn m…ôm…ô pris ot…ôk…ôike matol-p…ôn n…®ta e nat…®mnat tep…ôt, iu…ôhk…®r nat…®mnat rafin, m…ôm…ô ilat okotasim. K…ôn ok…ôm…ô n…®ta t…ôsaiu…ôn ron, k…ôn Uhg…®n okol t…ôsaf…ôl…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat.\f + \fr 9:22 \ft Lev 17:11\f*   
\p
\v 23 Tol n…ôhlan, n…®ta r…ôha nol…ôn sakrifais, in t…ômai…ôh o nol…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u, kotasim. M…ôto Nim…ô Tapol…ôn Asim ne nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôhan …ôh-ik…®n, ilat narm…® nat…®mnat m…®n …ôm\f + \fr 9:23 \ft Hip 8:5\f* it…ôm tat…ôpsen-p…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm koatat…®g e nego e neai. M…ôto n…ôfak…ôn o nat…®mnat it…ôm tol n…®p…ôt…® nat ag…®n-…ôh m…®n, it…ôm kotat…®g e nego e neai, n…®ta nat meg…ôh t…ôsahmen…ôn o nol…ôn ilat kotasim. Ok…ôike kol sakrifais kit it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s.  
\v 24 Iesu in t…ôsuw…®n…ôn im…ô e Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, it…ôm net…ômim …ôm k…ômotol. Nim…ô …ôh, in narm…® nat …ôm r…ôha Ik…®n Tasim Ik…®n pahrien …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai. M…ôto Iesu t…ômuw…®n e nego e neai, k…ôn roiu …ôh in tat…ôn-ip…ôn nat…®mnat r…ôhatat lan k…ôm Uhg…®n e n…®gan…ômt…®n.\f + \fr 9:24 \ft 1 Jon 2:1; Rom 8:34\f*  
\v 25 K…ôn nian Iesu t…ômol at…®p sakrifais e r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, in r…ôhan nol…ôn tol p…®s…®n e pris asol ag…®n u aup…ôn. E n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn u aup…ôn, pris asol ag…®n ot…ôk…ôike muw…®n im…ô e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n k…ôn mos n…®ta nat meg…ôh, s…ôn…ôm…ô n…®tan at…®p, mol sakrifais lan. T…ôike matol n…ôhlan e nup m…®n rafin. M…ôto Kristo t…ômuw…®n e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n e nego e neai, t…ômos at…®p n…®tan k…ôn mol sakrifais lan mau kiti…ôh …ôm k…ôn t…®nahmen.  
\v 26 Ok…ôm…ô Kristo t…ômatol sakrifais n…ôhlan e nup m…®n rafin, tahmen e pris m…®n u aup…ôn, in ot…ôk…ôike m…ôto nahm…ô…ôn nian tep…ôt t…ôtuoun e nian Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôtueint…ôn. M…ôto roiu, kitat k…®notat…®g e namnun nian, in t…ômiet-ar…ôpa mau kiti…ôh …ôm,\f + \fr 9:26 \ft Hip 9:12,28\f* m…ôm…ô otol at…®p sakrifais e r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn o nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat. K…ôn r…ôhan sakrifais, in namnun.  
\v 27 Kitat net…ômim, Uhg…®n t…®n…ôl…ôh…ôu nian …ôtuat…®p r…ôhatat kiti…ôh kiti…ôh m…ôm…ô okot…®m…®s lan, mau kiti…ôh …ôm. K…ôn uaris…®g lan un, in otakil r…ôhatat nol…ôn m…®n.\f + \fr 9:27 \ft 2 Kor 5:10\f*  
\v 28 E nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, Kristo t…ômol at…®p sakrifais lan, mau kiti…ôh …ôm,\f + \fr 9:28 \ft Hip 7:27; 9:12,26; 10:10\f* m…ôm…ô in otatipa-in t…ôfag…ô r…ôha net…ômim tep…ôt.\f + \fr 9:28 \ft Aes 53:12\f* M…ôto uaris…®g, nian otat…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n,\f + \fr 9:28 \ft Mat 16:27\f* in ot…ôsuwa-m…®n…ôn o nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat, m…ôto o nosmeg…ôh…ôn net…ômim it…ôm kot…ôsahgin, n…ôum…®s tatus ilat ron.\f + \fr 9:28 \ft 2 Tim 4:8\f*   
\c 10  
\s1 Sakrifais r…ôha Iesu, t…ômol nian kiti…ôh …ôm, k…ôn in t…®nahmen  
\m
\v 1 Nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôha Lou, ilat kotahmen e narm…® nat\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Kol 2:17; Hip 8:5\f* it…ôm ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn kotuwa, m…ôto toapoap. Ilat s…ôn…ôm…ô n…®p…ôt…® nat. E nup m…®n rafin pris m…®n koatol sakrifais. M…ôto nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô ilat koatol sakrifais, m…ôto Lou in t…ôruru nol…ôn i…ôfak m…®n it…ôm kotuwa o Uhg…®n kot…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®n, m…ôto-inun ilat narm…® sakrifais ag…®n, it…ôm toapoap.  
\v 2 Ok…ôm…ô sakrifais m…®n ilat kotahmen, mot…®tun nol…ôn net…ômim kot…ôtuat…®p. K…ôn i…ôfak m…®n kot…®tun n…ôl…ôh…ôu…ôn motap…ôs nol…ôn r…ôha sakrifais, m…ôto-inun n…®kilat t…®n…ôru…ôn r…ôk…®s mau kiti…ôh …ôm. K…ôn ok…ôm…ô t…®naf…ôl r…ôk…®s n…®kilat n…ôhlan, k…ôn ilat k…ôsot…ôto m…®n…ôn t…ôrat o r…ôhalat nol…ôn rat. M…ôto, k…ôp…ô, ilat koat…ôto …ôh t…ôrat.  
\v 3 Tol n…ôhlan, e nup m…®n rafin, ilat koatol pap sakrifais, m…ôto nat u tatol …ôm m…ôm…ô ilat okol k…ôsotaluin…ôn nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhalat,  
\v 4 m…ôto-inu n…®ta n…ôni ne kau in t…ôruru ag…®n nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat.\f + \fr 10:4 \ft Hip 9:12-14\f*   
\p
\v 5 Tol n…ôhlan, nian Kristo t…®nat…®mn…ô e n…ôtueint…ôn, in t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúIk nakap…ôs sakrifais m…®n ne nat…®mnat m…®n koatos-ip…ôn k…ôm ik.  
\q1 M…ôto ik n…ômol-p…ôn n…®p…ôt…®k kit m…ôm…ô ekuw…®n lan.‚Äù\f + \fr 10:5 \ft Hip 2:14; Sam 40:6-8\f*\fig |alt="bronze altar" src="HK00256B.TIF" size="span" loc="Heb 10:5" ref="Hip 10:5" \fig*   
\q1
\v 6 K…ômotuwaan …ôt…®p nat…®mnat e olta tahmen e n…ôfak…ôn r…ôhalat ot…®mn…ô ron ik,  
