\v 21 K…ôn pris asol ag…®n r…ôhatat, in et…ôm-iasol it…ôm tat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô\f + \fr 10:21 \ft Sek 6:13\f* e nim…ô r…ôha Uhg…®n, inun r…ôhan net…ômim.\f + \fr 10:21 \ft Hip 3:6\f*  
