\v 26 T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô koatem …ôskas…®k itat m…®n n…ôhlan, m…ôto-inu ok…ôm…ô kitat k…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s n…®pahrien…ôn, m…ôto k…ôsotol…ôn nat ag…®n lan, k…ôn kitat moat…ôk…ôike e nol…ôn rat, k…ôn tatol m…ôm…ô sakrifais kit m…®n t…®k…ô ag…®n o nos-ir…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôhatat.\f + \fr 10:26 \ft Hip 6:4-8; 2 Pita 2:20-21\f*  
\v 27 K…ôn ok…ôm…ô sakrifais kit m…®n t…®k…ô m…ô otos-ir…ôk…®s t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôhatat n…ôhlan, k…ôn nat kiti…ôh …ôm …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g. Inun, kitat koat…ôg…®n, moatasi…ôp, m…ôto-inun kitat kot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô kitat koat…ôsahgin …ôm nalp…®n…ôn …ôskas…®k, ne n…®g…ôm asol r…ôha nem…ôha r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm ot…ôk…ôike mus r…ôhan t…®k…®m…®r m…®n.\f + \fr 10:27 \ft 2 Tes 1:7-9; Hip 12:29\f*  
\v 28 E Lou oas r…ôha Moses aup…ôn, ok…ôm…ô suah kit tatol nat …ôpnap…®n e Lou, k…ôn et…ômim k…ôiu o k…®s…®l ok…ôhal…ôn-iar…ôp in, k…ôn suah u t…ôike m…®m…®s. Okol k…ôsotas…ôkitun…ôn.\f + \fr 10:28 \ft Dut 17:6,7\f*  
\v 29 ?M…ôto t…ôhrol e net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm koteguaf…ôl-eguaf…ôl N…ôt…® Uhg…®n?\f + \fr 10:29 \ft Hip 6:6\f* Uhg…®n t…ômol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha nasitu…ôn k…ôm kitat, k…ôn n…®ta Kristo t…ômol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn u t…ôtat…®g mat…ômeg…ôh.\f + \fr 10:29 \ft Mat 26:28\f* N…®tan …ôm un, t…®tun nol…ôn et…ômim tasim, k…ôn in et…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 10:29 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:5\f* ?M…ôto t…ôhrol e et…ômim it…ôm tatehm …ôpnap…®n …ôm n…®ta u, m…ôm…ô in s…ôn…ôm…ô nat iasim kit? ?Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n in tatoor n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôhan k…ôm net…ômim, m…ôto t…ôhrol e et…ômim it…ôm tat…ôn rat Narm…®n …ôh? Suah u, t…ôtuat…®p ag…®n …ôm m…ôm…ô nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhan in ot…ôskas…®k mapr…ôk…®s-in nalp…®n…ôn r…ôha et…ôm tat…ôtg…ôhl Lou r…ôha Moses.  
