\v 34 It…ômat n…ômotos moat…ôtul-p…ôn olat n…ôhlan, k…ôn nian k…ômotuw…®n e kalapus, k…ôn it…ômat n…ômotat…®g e n…ôrat…ôn m…ôs…®n r…ôhalat.\f + \fr 10:34 \ft Hip 13:3\f* K…ôn nian net…ômim k…ômotakl…ôh-in nat…®mnat m…®n r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn it…ômat n…®kit…ômat t…ômagien …ôm,\f + \fr 10:34 \ft 1 Pita 4:13\f* m…ôto-inu it…ômat n…ômot…®tun r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat nat…®mnat neen …ôh-ik…®n t…ôtat…®g, it…ôm in t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s, k…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n u, okol t…ôs…®k…ô…ôn nian kit.\f + \fr 10:34 \ft Hip 11:16; 1 Pita 1:4,5\f*   
\p
\v 35 In…ôh, in n…ôtou…ôn asol r…ôhat…ômat it…ôm Uhg…®n ot…ôpanos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat. K…ôn m…ôto-inun o nat w…®r m…®n …ôh it…ôm koat…ôm…ôhl aup…ôn-in it…ômat, t…ôs…ôw…®r…ôn m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…ômkar…ôp…ôn-in nahat…ôt…ô…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôhat…ômat.  
\v 36 It…ômat n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motol r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôf…ôm…ôh,\f + \fr 10:36 \ft Rom 5:3,4; Hip 12:1; Jem 1:3,4,12; 5:11\f* m…ôm…ô n…ôkoatol nat…®mnat it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike. K…ôn it…ômat on…ôpanotos nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm in t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm it…ômat.\f + \fr 10:36 \ft Hip 6:15; 9:15\f*  
