\v 39 M…ôto kitat u, k…ôsotol…ôn n…ôhlan. Kitat okol k…ôsotan t…ôl…®g-t…ôl…®g…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôr…ôk…®n kitat. K…ôp…ô. Kitat net…ôm r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Uhg…®n, m…ôm…ô kitat koatos n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.   
\c 11  
\s1 Nahat…ôt…ô…ôn  
\m
\v 1 ?Nat naka u, in nahat…ôt…ô…ôn? Kitat kot…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhatat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn e nat…®mnat m…®n u, it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa, k…ônu nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhatat in tatol m…ôm…ô kitat okot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat m…®n u, ilat n…®pahrien…ôn. Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô k…ôsotehm…ôn\f + \fr 11:1 \ft 2 Kor 4:18\f* nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôto kitat kot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô kitat okotos m…ôto-inun nahat…ôt…ô…ôn tat…ôg…ôtun n…ôhlan k…ôm kitat.  
\v 2 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ônuwi net…ôm m…®n u aup…ôn o r…ôhalat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn.   
\p
\v 3 Nahat…ôt…ô…ôn tatol m…ôm…ô kitat kot…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôghat …ôm, k…ôn ilat k…ômotat…®g.\f + \fr 11:3 \ft Jen 1\f* Nat…®mnat it…ôm kot…ôplan roiu, in t…ôm…ôsos…ôn nat kit it…ôm t…®nat…®g r…ôk…®s mol ilat lan.  
\v 4 Epel in t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, tol n…ôhlan in t…ômos-ip…ôn nat kit k…ôm Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s-in r…ôha Ken.\f + \fr 11:4 \ft Jen 4:4-5\f* K…ôn m…ôto-inu in t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n n…ôhlan, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô in et…ôm …ôtuat…®p kit, k…ôn n…®kin tagien o nos…ôn r…ôhan nat…®mnat. K…ôn nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô suah u t…ôm…®m…®s r…ôk…®s, m…ôto nol…ôn r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhan in tat…ôghat …ôh k…ôm kitat.\f + \fr 11:4 \ft Hip 12:24\f*   
\p
\v 5 K…ôn Inok t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, tol n…ôhlan in t…ôs…®m…®s…ôn. Uhg…®n t…ômos-ir…ôk…®s in e n…ôtueint…ôn u, m…ôm…ô otuw…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai. Net…ômim k…ôsot…ôplan m…®n…ôn, m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n t…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s.\f + \fr 11:5 \ft Jen 5:21-24\f* M…ôto nian Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôs…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s…ôn-…ôh, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôg…ôtun k…ôm in m…ôm…ô n…®kin tagien ron.  
\v 6 M…ôto ok…ôm…ô et…ômim t…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Uhg…®n, in t…ôsol…ôn Uhg…®n n…®kin tagien ron, m…ôto-inu nian suah kit tolkeike m…ôm…ô otuwa o Uhg…®n,\f + \fr 11:6 \ft Hip 7:19\f* in ot…ôk…ôike mahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ôtat…®g, k…ôn mat…ôtou net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm kotalkut o n…®tun…ôn in.   
\p
\v 7 Noah in t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, nian Uhg…®n t…ômat…ôn-ip…ôn nat…®mnat m…®n k…ôm in aup…ôn, it…ôm net…ômim k…ôsot…ôplan…ôn …ôh,\f + \fr 11:7 \ft Hip 11:1\f* Noah t…ômat…®siai-in, matol n…ôwian. K…ôn in t…ômil…ôk…®n nego asol kit\f + \fr 11:7 \ft Jen 6:13-22\f* m…ôm…ô otosmeg…ôh r…ôhan m…®n. E r…ôhan nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô Noah in t…ômatakil net…ômim. K…ôn e r…ôhan nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, Uhg…®n t…ômol in t…ôtuat…®p e n…®gan…ômt…®n.\f + \fr 11:7 \ft Jen 6:9\f*   
\p
\v 8 Epraham in t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, e nian Uhg…®n t…ômaun-in r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otuw…®n e n…ôpt…ôn p…®s…®n kit, in t…ômatol n…ôwia Uhg…®n. N…ôpt…ôn …ôh, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s r…ôk…®s k…ôm in m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm in. K…ôn Epraham t…ômiet, m…ôto in t…ôruru m…ôm…ô tatuw…®n hi…ô ne.  
\v 9 T…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n n…ôhlan, k…ôn m…ôtat…®g e n…ôpt…ôn u it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s aup…ôn m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm in.\f + \fr 11:9 \ft W…ôk 7:5\f* M…ôto t…ôm…ôtat…®g ik…®n …ôh e nim…ô tapol…ôn …ôm, tahmen …ôm e iap…®sp…®s kit. K…ôn Aisak ne Jekop it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn u k…ôm il…ôhal k…ôr…ôn, ilau m…®n k…ôm…ôtuat…®g …ôm e nim…ô tapol…ôn.\f + \fr 11:9 \ft Jen 12:1-8\f*  
\v 10 Epraham t…ômol nulan, m…ôto-inu in tat…ôsahgin m…ôm…ô otuw…®n e taon kit\f + \fr 11:10 \ft Hip 12:22; 13:14\f* it…ôm n…ôuk…ôt…®n ti…ôk…®s, ot…ôtat…®g tuw…ôh.\f + \fr 11:10 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 21:2, 14\f* Taon u, Uhg…®n …ôm t…ômol mak lan, k…ôn m…®nol r…ôk…®s t…ôtat…®g.\f + \fr 11:10 \ft Hip 11:16\f*   
\p
\v 11 Sera t…ôtahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô in t…®n…®p…®tagu…®hl ag…®n, m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô in otem…ôk. In t…ôm…®l…ôs n…ôt…®n u, m…ôto-inun in t…ômahat…ôt…ô lan m…ôm…ô otol n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôhan tuwa miet-ar…ôp.\f + \fr 11:11 \ft Suat…®p kit m…®n r…ôha n…ôuhlin…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u tol nulan. ‚ÄòEpraham t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, nat …ôpnap…®n Sera t…®n…®p…®tagu…®hl ag…®n, m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm in m…ôm…ô ot…ôp…®k-…ôp…®k. In t…ôm…®l…ôs n…ôt…®n u m…ôto-inu Epraham t…ômahat…ôt…ô e Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô in otol r…ôhan n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn tuwa miet-ar…ôp.‚Äô\f* \f + \fr 11:11 \ft Jen 17:19; 18:11-14; 21:2\f*  
\v 12 Epraham t…®nagu…®hl r…ôk…®s, ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn t…®m…®s,\f + \fr 11:12 \ft Rom 4:19\f* m…ôto noanol m…®n tep…ôt k…ômot…®s…®-p…ôn lan. Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô in et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm, m…ôto noanol m…®n …ôh r…ôhan, ilat tep…ôt tep…ôt, tahmen …ôm e m…ôhau …ôp…ôh e napu…ô ne n…®m…ôkl…ôk…®l …ôp…ôh it…ôh…ôi it…ôm k…ôruru nafin…ôn.\f + \fr 11:12 \ft Jen 22:17\f*   
\p
\v 13 Net…ôm m…®n u, ilat k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, m…ôto nian k…ômot…®m…®s, ilat k…ôm…ôsotos…ôn …ôh nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat.\f + \fr 11:13 \ft Hip 11:39\f* Ilat koat…ôplan nat…®mnat m…®n u m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat m…®n u koatan is…ôu …ôh olat, m…ôto n…®kilat tagien p…®k m…ôm…ô okot…ôplan.\f + \fr 11:13 \ft Mat 13:17\f* K…ôn ilat moat…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô koatat…®g e n…ôtueint…ôn u m…ôto ilat kotahmen …ôm e iap…®sp…®s m…®n …ôm.\f + \fr 11:13 \ft Jen 23:4; Lev 25:23; Fil 3:20; 1 Pita 1:17; 2:11\f* N…ôtueint…ôn u, s…ôn…ôm…ô in im…ôlat pahrien ik…®n.  
\v 14 Nian net…ômim koat…ôghat n…ôhlan, in tat…ôg…ôtun …ôsas …ôm, m…ôm…ô ilat koateg…ôs-in im…ôlat …ôtuat…®p ik…®n.  
\v 15 R…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôs…®t…ôl…®g-p…ôn…ôn e n…ôpt…ôn r…ôhalat aup…ôn, it…ôm k…®notap…ôs r…ôk…®s. Ok…ôm…ô n…®kilat tat…ôht n…ôhlan, kot…®tun n…®t…ôl…®g…ôn matuw…®n, m…ôto t…ôsol…ôn mihin.\f + \fr 11:15 \ft Jen 24:6-8\f*  
\v 16 Ilat kotolkeike im…ôlat ik p…®s…®n kit it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s, inun e nego e neai.\f + \fr 11:16 \ft 2 Tim 4:18\f* K…ôn o nat u, in t…ôsaul…®s-in…ôn\f + \fr 11:16 \ft Mak 8:38\f* m…ôm…ô ok…ôn m…ôm…ô in r…ôhalat Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 11:16 \ft Jen 26:24; 28:13; Eks 3:6, 15\f* K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô r…ôk…®s e taon kit\f + \fr 11:16 \ft Hip 11:10; 13:14\f* ik…®n …ôh.   
\p
\v 17-18 Epraham t…ômahat…ôt…ô e n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn m…®n it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm in. K…ôn n…ôghat…ôn kit it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s k…ôm in tol nulan, ‚ÄúK…ôn ok…ôn Aisak u m…ôm…ô in noanol …ôtuat…®p r…ôham,\f + \fr 11:17-18 \ft Jen 21:12; Rom 9:7\f* k…ôn e Aisak u, oekol r…ôham noanol otep…ôt otep…ôt.‚Äù M…ôto e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôha Epraham, nian Uhg…®n t…ômek asg…ôw…®n in, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôtul mat…®p o nohamnu…ôn n…ôt…®n noan kiti…ôh …ôm\f + \fr 11:17-18 \ft Nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô Epraham n…ôt…®n kit m…®n u Ismael, r…ôhan slef t…ôm…®l…ôs, m…ôto n…ôt…®n u Aisak kat…ôn m…ôm…ô in noan kiti…ôh …ôm m…ôto-inun Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s aup…ôn m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm Epraham, k…ôn in n…ôt…® p…ôtan …ôtuat…®p r…ôhan u Sera. ∆èplan-tu Jon 3:16\f* u Aisak m…ôm…ô otol sakrifais lan k…ôm Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 11:17-18 \ft Jen 22:1-10; Jem 2:21\f*\fig |alt="Abraham & Isaac" src="LB00291B.TIF" size="col" loc="Heb 11:17-19" ref="Hip 11:17-18" \fig*  
\v 19 M…ôto-inu Epraham n…®kin tat…ôht m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…®tun nol…ôn et…ômim t…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn.\f + \fr 11:19 \ft Rom 4:21; Jon 5:21\f* K…ôn in t…ômos m…®n net…®n, iu…ôhk…®r …ôm tahmen m…ôm…ô in t…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn.   
\p
\v 20 Aisak t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, t…ôm…ôfak m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôhan tuw…®n k…ôm Jekop ne Esao, mat…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa nian kit.\f + \fr 11:20 \ft Jen 27:27-29,39,40\f*   
\p
\v 21 Jekop t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, nian iu…ôhk…®r …ôm in t…®m…®s, in t…ôm…ôfak m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n ot…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm n…ôt…® Josep mil.\f + \fr 11:21 \ft Jen 48:1,8-22\f* In t…ôm…ôf kas…®k…®n, m…ôtul …ôm…ôhl-…ôm…ôhl, k…ôn in mat…ônwiwi Uhg…®n.   
\p
\v 22 Josep t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, iu…ôhk…®r …ôm in t…®m…®s, k…ôn in t…ômat…ôghat-in nian noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ok…ôpanotiet Ijip. K…ôn in t…ômat…ôn r…ôk…®s …ôm k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô okot…ôhrol e n…®k…®lk…®lin.\f + \fr 11:22 \ft Jen 50:24,25; Eks 13:19; Jos 24:32\f*   
\p
\v 23 Tata ne mama r…ôha Moses k…ômuahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, nian Moses t…ômaiir,\f + \fr 11:23 \ft Eks 2:2\f* ilau k…ômu…ôplan m…ôm…ô in suak…ôku w…®r kit, k…ôn ilau k…ômatu…ôhluaig-in o m…ôw…®g k…®s…®l. K…ôn ilau k…ôm…ôsuagin…ôn n…ôtg…ôhl…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha kig.\f + \fr 11:23 \ft Eks 1:16, 22\f*   
\p
\v 24 Moses t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, nian in t…ômol iahgin, k…ôn t…ôm…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô ok…ôn m…ôm…ô in n…ôt…® p…ôtan …ôk…ôku r…ôha Fero, kig r…ôha Ijip.\f + \fr 11:24 \ft Eks 2:10\f*  
\v 25 In t…ôm…ôsolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô ot…ôtat…®g e nagien…ôn e nol…ôn r…ôha t…ôfag…ô rat m…ôto-inu nagien…ôn r…ôha t…ôfag…ô, in t…ôtat…®g o nian …ôku…ôk…®r …ôm. In n…®kin t…ômagien m…ôm…ô otuw…®n moatat…®g ilat net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n, moat…ôto t…ôrat ilat min ilat.  
\v 26 N…®kin t…ômat…ôht m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô net…ômim okotalah-…ômnu\f + \fr 11:26 \ft Hip 13:13\f* in o Kristo it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa, k…ôn in okol t…ôsaul…®s…ôn. In n…®kin otagien t…ôhm…®n m…®n o nat u tapr…ôk…®s-in m…ôm…ô otat…ôto t…ôw…®r e nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn …ôp…ôh Ijip.\f + \fr 11:26 \ft Luk 14:33\f* In t…ômatol nulan m…ôto-inun nian rafin in tatuag-p…ôn o n…ôtou…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n otos-ip…ôn k…ôm in.\f + \fr 11:26 \ft Hip 10:35\f*  
\v 27 Moses in t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k n…ôhlan e Uhg…®n, k…ôn t…ômag…®m Ijip\f + \fr 11:27 \ft Eks 12:50, 51\f* m…ôs…ôgin…ôn kig u it…ôm nem…ôha tatol p…®k. In t…ôm…ôseirair…ôn m…®t…ôl…®g, in t…ôm…ôk…ôike matuw…®n, tahmen m…ôm…ô inu tat…ôplan Uhg…®n u, it…ôm et…ômim t…ôs…ôplan…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…®n.  
\v 28 T…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n n…ôhlan, k…ôn in t…ôm…ôtuoun nol…ôn lafet r…ôha Nuhagego-in…ôn. In t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel m…ôm…ô okot…ôk…ôike motorautin-p…ôn n…®ta sipsip e toa e nim…ô m…®n r…ôhalat. Okotol n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô nagelo it…ôm Uhg…®n otahl-ipa o nohamnu…ôn it…ôm,\f + \fr 11:28 \ft 1 Kor 10:10\f* in ot…ôsohamnu…ôn nen…ôt…®lat m…®n u n…ôman,\f + \fr 11:28 \ft Eks 12:21-23\f* it…ôm k…ômotaup…ôn kaiir.   
\p
\v 29 Noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. Tol n…ôhlan, ilat kot…®tun negu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn e N…®t…ôh…ôi Asi…ô it…ôm t…ômoor, k…ôn kotaliw…ôk lan tahmen …ôm e n…®t…ôn ias…ôk. M…ôto nian net…ôm Ijip k…ômotalkut o n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn ilat, k…ôn n…®t…ôh…ôi t…ôm…ôm…®k ilat, k…ôn kotamn…®m.\f + \fr 11:29 \ft Eks 14:21-31\f*   
\p
\v 30 Noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ilat kotaliw…ôk mot…®t…ôlau e fen…®s r…ôha Jeriko. Fen…®s u, k…ômol e k…ôpiel. Ilat koat…®t…ôlau, moat…®t…ôlau e fen…®s …ôh, m…ôtoarus-p…ôn nian sep…®n, k…ôn …ômun, fen…®s asol un, t…ôm…®t…ôg…®t m…®sas.\f + \fr 11:30 \ft Josua 6:12-20\f*   
\p
\v 31 Rehap u, p…ôtan e suat…®p, t…ômahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, n…®kin t…ômagien m…ôm…ô otos suah mil un noanol r…ôha Isrel mil, it…ôm k…ômueia anion m…ôm…ô oku…ôplan k…ôn miatun w…®r nat…®mnat ik…®n. Ilau k…ômuea e r…ôhan nim…ô.\f + \fr 11:31 \ft Jos 2:1-16\f* K…ôn o nat u, noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel ilat k…ôm…ôsotohamnu…ôn p…ôtan u nian ilat k…ômotohamnu net…ôm ik…®n …ôh it…ôm k…ômot…ôht n…ôwia Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 11:31 \ft Jos 2:1,9-14; 6:22-25; Jemes 2:25\f*   
\p
\v 32 M…ôto okol es…ôn…ôn tuw…®n t…ôhm…®n m…®n. Okol es…ôghat…ôn t…ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôn Kiteon,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft Jaj 6-8\f* ne Parak,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft Jaj 4-5\f* ne Samson,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft Jaj 13-16\f* ne Jefata,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft Jaj 11-12\f* ne Tef…®t,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft 1 Saml 16:1,13\f* ne Samuel,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft 1 Saml 1:20; 3:19‚Äî4:1\f* ne ien m…®n.  
\v 33 Ilat u k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan, ilat k…ômotol nat…®mnat tep…ôt. Ilat k…ômotit noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel motuw…®n mot…ôluag…®n ilat net…ôm ik p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n, k…ôn moatol win elat.\f + \fr 11:33 \ft 2 Saml 8:1-3\f* Ilat k…ômoatol nol…ôn …ôtuat…®p m…®n, k…ôn moatos nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat. K…ômotahtos…®g-in nohl…®n laion m…®n, m…ôm…ô ok…ôsotun…ôn ilat,\f + \fr 11:33 \ft Dan 6:22\f*  
\v 34 k…ôn ilat k…ômotoham…®s n…®g…ôm asol it…ôm tatu…ôp,\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Dan 3:19-27\f* k…ôn ilat motag…®m t…ônin net…ôm kot…ôm…ô okotohamnu ilat e nisa r…ôha n…ôluag…®n…ôn.\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Eks 18:4\f* Ilat r…ôhalat n…ôsan…ôn…ôn t…®k…ô, m…ôto Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm ilat.\f + \fr 11:34 \ft 2 King 20:7; Jaj 16:28\f* K…ôn ilat koatol win e mopael m…®n r…ôha n…®m…ôpt…ôn p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n.\f + \fr 11:34 \ft Jajes 15:8\f*  
\v 35 N…®p…®tan neen …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n, k…ôn tol n…ôhlan Uhg…®n tatol nen…ôt…®lat kotaiir-pa m…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn.\f + \fr 11:35 \ft 1 King 17:22, 23; 2 King 4:36, 37\f* M…ôto net…ômim neen …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm kotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k e Uhg…®n. M…ôto ilat koteg…ôhan-in r…ôhalat t…®k…®m…®r m…®n koatol n…ôrat…ôn ne nahm…ô…ôn k…ôm ilat e n…®p…ôt…®lat, k…ôn n…®kilat t…ôs…ôht…ôn nat u. Ilat k…ôm…ôsotap…ôs…ôn r…ôhalat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, m…ôm…ô r…ôhalat t…®k…®m…®r m…®n okot…®k…®s ilat. Ilat koatahat…ôt…ô m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n in otol ilat kot…ômeg…ôh m…®n e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn kit it…ôm t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s.  
\v 36 K…ôn ilat neen, net…ômim koatalah …ôsan elat, k…ôn koatalis-alis ilat.\f + \fr 11:36 \ft Jer 20:2; 37:15\f* K…ôn ilat neen, net…ômim koat…ôlis …ôtain ilat e sen, k…ôn moat…ômki-p…ôn ilat e kalapus.\f + \fr 11:36 \ft Jen 39:20\f*  
\v 37 Ilat neen, k…ômaht…®mnu ilat e k…ôpiel ap…®n,\f + \fr 11:37 \ft 2 Kron 24:21\f* k…ôn ilat neen, net…ômim k…ômot…ôm…®k so…ô r…ôha n…ôtahl…ôn n…®g, mot…ôtat…®p n…®p…ôt…®lat n…ôwtain k…ôiu, motohamnu ilat. K…ôn ilat neen, k…ôm…ôtamnu ilat e nisa r…ôha n…ôluag…®n…ôn.\f + \fr 11:37 \ft 1 King 19:10; Jer 26:23\f* K…ôn ilat neen koatuw…®n …ôm e nuw…®g…® n…ôni ne sipsip.\f + \fr 11:37 \ft 2 King 1:8\f* Ilat ian-rat m…®n ag…®n, nian rafin net…ômim koat…ôr…ôk…®n ilat, moatol t…ôrat ag…®n elat.  
\v 38 Ilat, net…ôm w…®r m…®n. N…ôtueint…ôn u, t…ôsahmen…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat okotat…®g ik…®n. M…ôto ilat k…ômoatat…®g …ôpnap…®n …ôm, …ôp…ôh ik…®n taru…ôn-aru…ôn ik…®n, ne e n…®tot m…®n, ne e n…®p…ôg k…ôpiel m…®n,\f + \fr 11:38 \ft 1 King 18:4; 19:9\f* ne n…®p…ôg m…®n …ôp…ôh e n…®s…®p.   
\p
\v 39 Net…ôm m…®n u, ilat rafin k…ômotahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k nulan e Uhg…®n, k…ôn in t…ômos-ip…ôn n…ôr…®g w…®r k…ôm ilat.\f + \fr 11:39 \ft Hip 11:2, 4\f* M…ôto ilat k…ôm…ôsotos…ôn …ôh nat u\f + \fr 11:39 \ft E ves 33 kitat kot…ôplan m…ôm…ô net…ôm m…®n u neen k…ômoatos nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat. M…ôto n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn kit …ôh-ik…®n it…ôm k…ôsotos…ôn …ôh. Ilat kot…ôtag-p…ôn o nian it…ôm Uhg…®n otahl-ipa Kristo tuwa, m…ôto ilat u, k…ôm…ôsotehm…ôn e r…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn.\f* it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s r…ôk…®s m…ôm…ô otos-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat,\f + \fr 11:39 \ft Hip 11:13; 10:36\f*  
\v 40 m…ôto-inu in t…®nol r…ôk…®s nalp…ôkau…ôn kit r…ôhan, m…ôm…ô in otol t…ôw…®r mapr…ôk…®s k…ôm kitat. K…ôn e n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhan, in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…®lp…®n kitat min ilat u aup…ôn, m…ôm…ô kitat min ilat …ôm, okot…ôtoarus ahmen ahmen …ôm mak e namnun naiu…ôn.\f + \fr 11:40 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 6:11; Hip 2:10\f*\f + \fr 11:40 \ft Suat…®p kit m…®n r…ôha n…ôn…ôn ‚Äúokot…ôtoarus ahmen ahmen …ôm mak,‚Äù tol nulan, ‚Äúkitat min ilat m…®n un, okol k…ôl…ôh kitat kot…ôtuat…®p ag…®n.‚Äù\f*   
\c 12  
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ôt…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in  //  nen…ôt…®n m…®n  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn net…ôm m…®n u, ilat tep…ôt tep…ôt, koatat…®g k…®t…ôlau e kitat, koat…ôtul-ar…ôp o Uhg…®n, moatahat…ôt…ô …ôskas…®k lan, k…ôn r…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn in tat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhatat. O nat u, p…ôs kot…ôl…®n rafin nat f…®g…ôm it…ôm otask…ôl…®m …ôtain itat m…ôm…ô k…ôsotaiu p…®k…ôn, ne t…ôfag…ô rat it…ôm tat…ôper-ip…ôn e kitat. K…ôn p…ôs kitat kotaiu\f + \fr 12:1 \ft 1 Kor 9:24\f* m…ôsot…ôpou-in…ôn\f + \fr 12:1 \ft Hip 10:36\f* naiu…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu aup…ôn-in kitat.  
\v 2 Kot…®tun nol…ôn nian n…®gan…ômt…®tat otat…ôtul-p…ôn …ôm o Iesu,\f + \fr 12:2 \ft Sam 25:15\f* it…ôm in n…ôuk…ôt…® nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhatat,\f + \fr 12:2 \ft Hip 2:15\f* k…ôn inun it…ôm otol m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôtoarus mak e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhatat. P…ôs kitat n…®kitat otu…ôh nol…ôn r…ôha Iesu, inun in r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn kaif…ôm…ôh, nian in t…ôm…®m…®s e n…®g k…ôluau, k…ôn m…ôto nahm…ô…ôn.\f + \fr 12:2 \ft Fil 2:8,9; Hip 2:9\f* M…ôto in t…ômol nat …ôpnap…®n lan, meg…ôhan-in naul…®s…ôn r…ôha n…®m…®s…ôn e n…®g k…ôm…ôluau, m…ôto-inu t…ômol r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôskas…®k o nagien…ôn it…ôm in ot…ôpanos. K…ôn roiu, in tat…ôp…ôl…ôh e r…ôhn mat…®p Uhg…®n u in Kig,\f + \fr 12:2 \ft Mak 16:19\f* ik…®n nep…ôt…ôn ne n…®siaii…ôn t…ôtat…®g ik…®n.  
\v 3 T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat otat…ôht Iesu, ne r…ôhan n…ôtul …ôskas…®k…ôn e nian iol t…ôfag…ô m…®n k…ômot…ôrakin-p…ôn n…ôghat…ôn rat m…®n k…ôm in, m…ôm…ô n…®kit…ômat ot…ôs…ôpou…ôn\f + \fr 12:3 \ft Kal 6:9; Nol ∆èp…ôn 2:3\f* k…ôn motap…ôs nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.   
\p
\v 4 Ek…®tun m…ôm…ô it…ômat, noat…ôluag…®n o noh r…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, m…ôto it…ômat kit t…®k…ô it…ôm n…®tan t…ômai…ôh o n…ôluag…®n…ôn u.\f + \fr 12:4 \ft Hip 10:32-34\f*  
