\q1 m…ôto in ot…ôpan…ôw…®r m…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 12:13 \ft Aes 35:3; Hip 10:36-39; 12:1-3; Prov 4:26\f*   
\s1 Et…ôm t…ôsahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Uhg…®n, in ot…ôk…ôike mos nalp…®n…ôn  
\p
\v 14 Otalkut m…ôm…ô onakat…®g w…®r it…ômat net…ômim rafin e n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn.\f + \fr 12:14 \ft Rom 14:19\f* K…ôn motalkut m…ôm…ô n…ôkotol it…ômat m…ôm…ô r…ôhat…ômat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn tasim.\f + \fr 12:14 \ft Rom 6:22\f* Et…ômim it…ôm t…ôsasim…ôn, okol t…ôs…ôplan…ôn n…®gan…ômt…® Ier…ôm…ôr…ô nian kit.\f + \fr 12:14 \ft Mat 5:8\f*  
\v 15 Ot…ôto w…®r it…ômat m…ôm…ô it…ômat kit it…ôm t…ôtaiu matuw…®n ot…ôpou e n…ôlug…® suat…®p, k…ôn m…ôsos…ôn n…ôw…®r…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 12:15 \ft Hip 3:12; 4:1\f* Ot…ôto w…®r m…®n it…ômat m…ôm…ô nok…® n…®g akona kit\f + \fr 12:15 \ft Dut 29:18; Hip 3:12\f* in ot…ôsuw…®n…ôn e n…®kit…ômat, k…ôn m…ôwi…ô, mol noan tep…ôt e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat. K…ôn nahuin t…®tun n…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôha net…ôm iasim neen m…®n.  
\v 16 Oat…ôto w…®r it…ômat m…ôm…ô suah kit t…ôsit …ôpnap…®n…ôn i…ôrman o p…ôtan.\f + \fr 12:16 \ft 1 Kor 6:18\f* It…ômat kit ot…ôsahmen…ôn e Esao u, r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn t…ôs…ôtuat…®p…ôn, in tatol nat …ôpnap…®n e Uhg…®n. In t…ômaup…ôn maiir, m…ôto in t…ômol-sal…®m-in nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha suak…ôku it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn maiir.\f + \fr 12:16 \ft Jen 25:29-34\f* M…ôto n…ômt…® nat u, in t…ômol-sal…®m-in, in nagw…ôn…ôn it…ôm t…ômun mau kiti…ôh …ôm.  
\v 17 It…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô uaris…®g, n…®kin ot…ôpanuw…®n m…®n e nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha n…ômt…®-n…®p…®n. K…ôn t…ômalkut p…®k m…ôm…ô r…ôhan tata ot…ôfak m…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn kit k…ôm in. M…ôto nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô t…ôm…ôtas…ôk p…®k pap ron,\f + \fr 12:17 \ft Jen 27:30-40\f* m…ôto okol t…ôs…ôuhlin…ôn n…®kin …ôh-roiu, k…ôn r…ôhan tata okol t…ôs…ôfak…ôn m…ôhlman n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm in.   
