\p
\v 18-21 Aup…ôn ik…®n, noanol m…®n r…ôha Isrel, k…ômotuw…®n e n…®tot asol u Sinae, e n…ôtueint…ôn u. K…ôn ik…®n …ôh, k…ômot…ôplan n…®g…ôm it…ôm tatu…ôp, k…ôn napin…ôp…ôn asol t…ômeiuaiu m…®r…ôfin nat, k…ôn k…ômot…ôto n…®m…ôtag asol ne t…ôwi t…ôtag…ôt …ôf…ôm…ôh,\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft Eks 19:12-22; 20:18; Dut 4:11\f* k…ôn k…ômot…ôto n…ôwian kit tat…ôghat k…ôm ilat.\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft Dut 4:12\f* K…ôn nian k…ômot…ôt…ôl…®g-in r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn m…®n, k…ôn ilat k…ômoat…ôn …ôskas…®k m…ôm…ô ilat kotap…ôs ag…®n-…ôh n…ôto m…®n…ôn n…ôwian u.\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft Eks 20:18-19; Dut 5:5,25; 18:16\f* K…ômot…ôgin motasi…ôp o n…ôghat…ôn u, t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOk…ôm…ô nat meg…ôh …ôm kit otuw…®n e n…®tot u, m…ôto it…ômat on…ôkot…ôike moataht e k…ôpiel ap…®n motaht…®mnu t…®m…®s.‚Äù\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft Eks 19:12,13\f* Nian Moses t…ôm…ôplan nat…®mnat m…®n u, in m…®n t…ôm…ôto t…ôrat k…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo en…ôg…®n u en…ôg…®n, m…®n…ôtasi…ôp.‚Äù\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft Dut 9:19\f*  
\p M…ôto it…ômat n…ôsotuwam…ôn ik…®n-u.\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft Eks 19:16-19; 20:18-21; Dut 4:11-12\f*   
\p
\v 22 It…ômat n…ômotuwa e n…®tot u Saeon,\f + \fr 12:22 \ft Aes 24:23; 60:14; Nol ∆èp…ôn 14:1\f* ne taon asol\f + \fr 12:22 \ft Hip 11:10; 13:14; Mat 16:16\f* u ima Uhg…®n ik…®n it…ôm tat…ômeg…ôh, t…ôtat…®g t…ôtat…®g. Inun Jerusalem wi …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai,\f + \fr 12:22 \ft Kal 4:26\f* u nagelo m…®n taosan taosan k…ômu…ôf…®m…®n ilat ik…®n o nagien…ôn asol.  
\v 23 K…ôn it…ômat n…ômotuwa e nu…ôf…®m…®n…ôn asol r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm kotahmen e net…ôm k…ômotaup…ôn kaiir u r…ôhan m…®n,\f + \fr 12:23 \ft Eks 4:22\f* n…ôrg…®lat k…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s e nego e neai.\f + \fr 12:23 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 20:12\f* K…ôn it…ômat n…ômotuwa o Uhg…®n, it…ôm ot…ôpanakil net…ômim rafin.\f + \fr 12:23 \ft Jen 18:25; Sam 94:2\f* It…ômat n…ômotuwa motol kiti…ôh it…ômat narm…® net…ôm …ôtuat…®p it…ôm k…®not…®m…®s r…ôk…®s, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…®nol ilat k…®not…ôtoarus mak.\f + \fr 12:23 \ft Fil 3:12\f*\f + \fr 12:23 \ft Suat…®p kit m…®n o n…ôuhlin…ôn n…ôghat…ôn u, ‚ÄúUhg…®n t…®nol ilat k…®not…ôtoarus mak‚Äù tol nulan, ‚ÄúUhg…®n t…®nol ilat k…®not…ôtuat…®p ag…®n.‚Äù\f*  
\v 24 It…ômat n…ômotuwa o Iesu u, in suat…®p r…ôha n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn wi r…ôha nasitu…ôn u it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol k…ôm itat. K…ôn n…ômotuwa o n…®ta Iesu, it…ôm in t…ômorautin-p…ôn\f + \fr 12:24 \ft Hip 9:19; 10:22; 1 Pita 1:2\f* mol it…ômat nakotasim. N…®ta …ôh in t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp nat…®mnat m…®n u it…ôm kot…ôw…®r motapr…ôk…®s-in nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm n…®ta Epel t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp.\f + \fr 12:24 \ft Jen 4:10; Hip 11:4\f*\f + \fr 12:24 \ft N…®ta Epel in t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otol nalp…®n…ôn, m…ôto n…®ta Iesu t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n otoh r…ôk…®s nalp…®n…ôn.\f*   
\p
\v 25 O nat…®mnat m…®n u, oat…ôto w…®r it…ômat, m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôsot…ôuhlin…ôn m…ôntaat…ômat o Uhg…®n\f + \fr 12:25 \ft Hip 3:12\f* u tat…ôghat k…ôm it…ômat.\f + \fr 12:25 \ft Hip 1:1\f* M…ôto-inu Moses, in et…ômim …ôm. K…ôn kitat kot…®tun m…ôm…ô net…ôm aup…ôn k…ôm…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn r…ôhan n…ôghat…ôn o n…ôhgaiir…ôn elat. Ilat k…ôm…ôsotag…®m r…ôk…®s…ôn e nalp…®n…ôn r…ôhalat. ?K…ôn ok…ôm…ô tol n…ôhlan, k…ôn okahrol kitat ok…ôm…ô k…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn e nego e neai muwa m…ôm…ô ot…ôhgaiir etat?\f + \fr 12:25 \ft Hip 2:2,3; 10:29\f* ?Kitat okotag…®m r…ôk…®s-in ahrol nulan?  
\v 26 Nian aup…ôn, n…ôwia Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôloal e n…ôpt…ôn.\f + \fr 12:26 \ft Eks 19:18\f* M…ôto roiu …ôh, t…ôm…ôn-i…ôk…®s k…ôm itat m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n, io ek…ôloal m…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn. K…ôn o nian …ôh, s…ôn…ôm…ô n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm ekat…®gt…®g lan tasi…ôp, m…ôto neai m…®n otasi…ôp-asi…ôp m…ôloal.‚Äù\f + \fr 12:26 \ft Hag 2:6\f*  
\v 27 Nian Uhg…®n tat…ôghat-in m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúNian kit m…®n …ôh-ik…®n,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n un m…ôm…ô in otat…®gt…®g\f + \fr 12:27 \ft Aes 34:4; 54:10; 1 Kor 7:31; Hip 1:11,12; 2 Pita 3:10; 1 Jon 2:17\f* e nat…®mnat r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn …ôm it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômol, m…ôm…ô otoh r…ôk…®s ilat. Otoh r…ôk…®s n…ôhlan nat…®mnat, m…ôm…ô nat…®mnat it…ôm ok…ôsot…ôloal…ôn, ilat okotat…®g, k…ôn inun, nat…®mnat it…ôm okotat…®g lil…®n.   
\p
\v 28 O nat u, t…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôn tagkiu o Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu kitat koatos nego r…ôha Uhg…®n u, k…ôruru n…ôloal-…ôloal…ôn lan, k…ôn okol t…ôsiet…ôn nian kit.\f + \fr 12:28 \ft Sam 15:5; Dan 2:44\f* T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô kitat kot…ôfak k…ôm in, e nol…ôn it…ôm n…®kin tagien lan, m…ôm…ô kitat okot…®siai-in, k…ôn mot…ôgin m…®n,\f + \fr 12:28 \ft Mal 2:5; 4:2\f*  
\v 29 m…ôto-inun Uhg…®n r…ôhatat, in tahmen e n…®g…ôm asol kit it…ôm tatuwaan …ôt…®p nat…®mnat rafin.\f + \fr 12:29 \ft Eks 24:17; Dut 4:24; 9:3; Sam 97:3; Aes 33:14; 2 Tes 1:7\f*   
\c 13  
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn  
\m
\v 1 T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô n…ôkot…ôk…ôike …ôh moatol nolkeike…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…®n tahmen e piat…ômat m…®n.\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Rom 12:10\f*  
\v 2 Sotaluin…ôn nehm…ôn iap…®sp…®s m…®n it…ôm koatuwa imat…ômat ik…®n.\f + \fr 13:2 \ft Job 31:32; Mat 25:35; Rom 12:13\f* !Ok…ôm-naka ilat nagelo m…®n! Net…ômim neen it…ôm k…ômoatol nulan, ilat k…ômoatehm w…®r net…ômim, m…ôsot…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat nagelo m…®n.\f + \fr 13:2 \ft Jen 18:1-33\f*  
\v 3 Sotaluin…ôn net…ôm kotat…®g e kalapus.\f + \fr 13:3 \ft Mat 25:36; Hip 10:34\f* N…®kit…ômat otatu…ôh ilat, m…ôtahm…ô olat tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inun ik m…®n n…ôk…ôtat…®g e kalapus. Ot…ôto k…ôl…ôh nahm…ô…ôn e n…®kit…ômat, it…ômat net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm katol t…ôrat elat, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inun ik nat…ôto nahm…ô…ôn e n…®p…ôt…®m at…®p.   
