\v 10 R…ôhatat olta tat…®g. M…ôto pris m…®n it…ôm koatol w…ôk r…ôhalat …ôp…ôh im…ô e tapol…ôn r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn u,\f + \fr 13:10 \ft Hip 8:5\f* ilat u, k…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn ilat m…ôm…ô okotun\f + \fr 13:10 \ft 1 Kor 9:13; 10:18\f* nagw…ôn…ôn\f + \fr 13:10 \ft Jon 6:48-58\f* kit e olta u r…ôhatat.\f + \fr 13:10 \ft ‚ÄúNagw…ôn…ôn‚Äù it…ôm katol sakrifais lan e ‚Äúr…ôhatat olta‚Äù inun Kristo p…®s…®n …ôm (Jon 6:48-58). Pris m…®n aup…ôn, ilat k…ômot…®tun nun…ôn noanuw…ôhg…®n nat meg…ôh m…®n e sakrifais m…®n neen ilat koatol o nos-ip…ôn…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n. M…ôto k…ôseg…ôhan-in…ôn k…ôm ilat o ‚Äúnun…ôn‚Äù Kristo, n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô k…ôsotos…ôn ron.\f*   
\p
\v 11 E nol…ôn r…ôha pris asol ag…®n, nian in tatohamnu r…ôk…®s nat meg…ôh, k…ôn matos n…®tan k…ôn muw…®n …ôp…ôh im…ô e Ik…®n Tasim Ag…®n Ik…®n, k…ôn mos-ip…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n o naf…ôl r…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô r…ôha net…ômim.\f + \fr 13:11 \ft Lev 16:15\f* M…ôto uaris…®g, kat…®l…ôs-iar…ôp nat meg…ôh u …ôp…ôh ihlu…ô ik…®n e nim…ô tapol…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat, motaan …ôt…®p.\f + \fr 13:11 \ft Eks 29:14; Lev 4:12,21; 9:11; 16:27\f*  
\v 12 E nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, Iesu t…ômiet r…ôk…®s e taon,\f + \fr 13:12 \ft Jon 19:17\f* k…ôn ik…®n …ôh in t…ôm…ôto nahm…ô…ôn e n…®p…ôt…®n, k…ôn m…®m…®s ik…®n …ôh, m…ôm…ô n…®tan\f + \fr 13:12 \ft Rom 3:25\f* t…®tun naf…ôl r…ôk…®s…ôn t…ôfag…ô rat r…ôha net…ômim, mol ilat kot…ôtuat…®p, motasim, m…ôm…ô ilat r…ôha Uhg…®n.\f + \fr 13:12 \ft Efes 5:26\f*  
\v 13 Tol nulan, p…ôs kitat kotol m…ôm…ô inu okotiet ihlu…ô im…ôtat ik…®n, motol kiti…ôh kitat min …ôp…ôh ihlu…ô.\f + \fr 13:13 \ft Luk 9:23\f* K…ôn okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôtul mat…®p m…ôm…ô net…ômim okotol naul…®s…ôn k…ôm itat, tahmen …ôm m…ô inun, k…ômotol mihin lan.\f + \fr 13:13 \ft Hip 11:26\f*  
\v 14 E n…ôtueint…ôn u, r…ôhatat kit taon …ôtuat…®p im…ôtat ik…®n t…®k…ô, it…ôm ot…ôtat…®g lil…®n.\f + \fr 13:14 \ft Hip 12:27\f* M…ôto kitat koateg…ôs-in r…ôhatat taon …ôtuat…®p it…ôm kot…®tun m…ôm…ô ot…ôpanuwa.\f + \fr 13:14 \ft Fil 3:20; Hip 11:10; 12:22\f*   
