\v 15 Tol nulan, e nasitu…ôn r…ôha Iesu, p…ôs kitat kotos-ip…ôn sakrifais r…ôhatat k…ôm Uhg…®n nian rafin.\f + \fr 13:15 \ft 1 Pita 2:5\f* Sakrifais m…®n u r…ôhatat, inun, okoat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Uhg…®n nian rafin, moat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôrg…®n.\f + \fr 13:15 \ft Sam 50:2-15; Hos 14:2; Aes 57:19\f*  
