\v 21 in otos-ip…®n…ô nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n rafin k…ôm it…ômat, it…ôm otol it…ômat n…ôkotahmen o nol…ôn nat it…ôm in tolkeike. K…ôn iat…ôfak m…ôm…ô, Uhg…®n otol w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhatat kiti…ôh kiti…ôh,\f + \fr 13:21 \ft Fil 2:13\f* k…ôn e nasitu…ôn r…ôha Iesu Kristo, in otol r…ôhatat nol…ôn t…ôw…®r t…ôw…®r, k…ôn n…®kin otagien p…®k ron. K…ôn p…ôs kot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…® Kristo il…®s nian rafin, matuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô. ∆èw…ôh.\f + \fr 13:21 \ft Rom 11:36\f*   
\p
\v 22 Piak m…®n ne w…®n…®k m…®n. Naoa u r…ôhak t…ôs…ôf…ôm…ôh p…®k…ôn. M…ôto iak…ôtap…ôh …ôskas…®k ot…ômat m…ôm…ô, otol-tu r…ôhat…ômat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôf…ôm…ôh m…®n m…ôm…ô nakot…ôt…ôl…®g-in r…ôhak n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.   
\p
\v 23 Iakolkeike m…ôm…ô on…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô pi…ôtat u Timoti, ilat k…ômot…®l…ôs-iar…ôp in e kalapus. Ok…ôm…ô in otuwa u…ôhai …ôm, k…ôn it…®mlau min, ekiamn…ô.   
\p
\v 24 It…ômat ot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ôm-iasol m…®n r…ôhat…ômat, ne i…ôfak m…®n u imat…ômat ik…®n. Net…ôm Itali k…ômot…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm it…ômat.   
